													$('jt_map_enlarge').show();">Smaller map</a><a id=jt_map_street_zoom href=javascript:void(0); onclick=map.setZoom(15);>Zoom to Street</a><br><br><div id=jt_map style="width: 99%; height: 200px; border: 1px solid black;"></div></div></div></div><div id=jt_job_summary><p><em>This is not an entry-level position.</em></p><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><th>Job ID:</th><td>7431950</td></tr><tr><th>Position Title:</th><td>Systems/Software Engr VI</td></tr><tr><th>Min Education:</th><td>H.S. Diploma/Equivalent</td></tr><tr><th>Industry:</th><td>Other</td></tr></table></td><td><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><th>Posted:</th><td>December 5, 2010</td></tr><tr><th>Job Function:</th><td>Information Technology</td></tr><tr><th>Job Type:</th><td>Full-Time</td></tr><tr><th>Salary:</th><td>Yearly Salary)</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></div><div id=jt_job_contact><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><th>Apply URL:</th><td><a href="http://ars2.equest.com/?response_id=fc378eab22acecda996c653732ae203a">http://ars2.equest.com/?response_id=fc378eab22acec...</a></td></tr></table></td><td> &nbsp; </td></tr></table></div><div id=jt_job_description> HP is a leading global provider of products, technologies, solutions and services to consumers and business. The company's offerings span IT infrastructure, personal computing and access devices, global services, and imaging and printing. Our $4 billion annual R&D investment fuels the invention of products, solutions and new technologies so we can better serve customers and enter new markets. We invent, engineer and deliver technology solutions that drive business value, create social value and improve the lives of our customers. StorageWorks Entry NAS is a critical business unit within the Unified Storage Division (USD), providing Microsoft Windows-based X1000 and X3000 Network Storage Systems.&nbsp; As a Expert System/Software Engineer in the Entry NAS organization, you will participate in the development of innovative storage products that integrate standard server platforms and operating systems with HP value-add storage management software by HP and external partners. Scope of role may expand to include additional Windows-based storage offerings over time.<br> &nbsp;<br> Responsibilities include:<br> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Serve as lead architect for the StorageWorks X1000 and X3000 Network Storage Systems, helping to define roadmap and program deliverables and driving successful, timely, high-quality completion of committed<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;program deliverables.<br> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lead technical relationship with Microsoft and track Microsoft software offerings, understanding their implications for our products.<br> 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Track industry trends, competitor offerings, HP hardware plans, and HP product plans, working cooperatively with Marketing, ISS, USD sibling labs, and other key partners to help drive future product directions<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; and increase Entry NAS integration with other USD products.<br> 4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Stay abreast of current technologies, guiding team&#39;s technical decisions and ensuring that product designs are effective, robust, and maintainable.<br> 5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Seek to improve go-to-market success via technical support of sales-performance testing, certification, white papers, big deal support, etc.<br> 6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Evaluate current processes in light of new and changing requirements. Evolve and invent new tactics and strategies as necessary to maintain and improve overall project effectiveness, productivity, and competitive<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; advantage.<br> 7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Seek to understand customer needs, apply your customer knowledge to business decisions, and ultimately increase customer satisfaction.<br> 8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mentor and coach team members to increase the overall success of the team and overall quality of the deliverables.<br> &nbsp;<br> &nbsp; Education:&nbsp; Bachelor&#39;s (undergraduate), Master&#39;s (graduate) or Ph.D. (post-graduate) degree in a technical discipline such as Computer Science, Information Technology, Computer Engineering, or Electrical Engineering.<br> &nbsp;<br> &nbsp;Qualifications:<br> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proven ability to work with partners and drive collaboration.<br> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proven technical leadership skills: storage technologies and applications, Windows Storage Server, software development.<br> 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience configuring computer systems and managing networks.<br> 4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Effective troubleshooting skills.<br> 5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strong written and verbal communication skills.<br> 6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ability to research technical issues and generate creative/innovative solutions.<br> 7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proven ability to deliver multi-person/multi-site, complex, hardware/software products and to help the team develop requirements, designs, schedule estimates, and test plans that will enable successful project<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; execution.<br> 8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Demonstrable programming skills in C and/or C++, as well as scripting.<br> 9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Software development, object-oriented design and/or software test knowledge.<br> 10.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Self directed, highly motivated, strong work ethic.<br> &nbsp;<br> Desired qualifications:<br> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Understanding of computer architecture.<br> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience with Linux or HP-UX operating systems.<br> &nbsp; <img src="http://ars2.equest.com/?response_id=fc378eab22acecda996c653732ae203a&amp;view" alt=" " width=1 height=1></div><a id=jt_return_to_search_2 class=jt_return_to_search href="/c2/search.cfm?site%5Fid=1#job7431950">&laquo;&nbsp;Return to Results</a></div></td></tr></table><iframe src="/c/includes/jvi.cfm?site_id=1&job=7431950" style=display:none;width:1px;height:1px;></iframe></div></td></tr></table></div><div id=jt_footer> Copyright &copy; 2007 JobTarget, All Rights Reserved.<br><a href=http://www.jobtargetjobfinder.com>Job Seeker Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtarget.com/corp/products-services/job-board-solutions/ >Job Board Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtargetoneclick.com>Recruiting Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=/c2/tou.cfm>Terms of Usage</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtarget.com/corp/privacy-policy/ >Privacy Policy</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtarget.com/corp/company/company-overview/ >About JobTarget</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/c2/support.cfm?site_id=1">Contact JobTarget</a></div></body></html><div id=overDiv style="position: absolute; display: none; z-index: 1000;"></div>

