ge Systems.&nbsp; As a Expert System/Software Engineer in the Entry NAS organization, you will participate in the development of innovative storage products that integrate standard server platforms and operating systems with HP value-add storage management software by HP and external partners. Scope of role may expand to include additional Windows-based storage offerings over time.<br> &nbsp;<br> Responsibilities include:<br> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Serve as lead architect for the StorageWorks X1000 and X3000 Network Storage Systems, helping to define roadmap and program deliverables and driving successful, timely, high-quality completion of committed<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;program deliverables.<br> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lead technical relationship with Microsoft and track Microsoft software offerings, understanding their implications for our products.<br> 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Track industry trends, competitor offerings, HP hardware plans, and HP product plans, working cooperatively with Marketing, ISS, USD sibling labs, and other key partners to help drive future product directions<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; and increase Entry NAS integration with other USD products.<br> 4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Stay abreast of current technologies, guiding team&#39;s technical decisions and ensuring that product designs are effective, robust, and maintainable.<br> 5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Seek to improve go-to-market success via technical support of sales-performance testing, certification, white papers, big deal support, etc.<br> 6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Evaluate current processes in light of new and changing requirements. Evolve and invent new tactics and strategies as necessary to maintain and improve overall project effectiveness, productivity, and competitive<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; advantage.<br> 7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Seek to understand customer needs, apply your customer knowledge to business decisions, and ultimately increase customer satisfaction.<br> 8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mentor and coach team members to increase the overall success of the team and overall quality of the deliverables.<br> &nbsp;<br> &nbsp; Education:&nbsp; Bachelor&#39;s (undergraduate), Master&#39;s (graduate) or Ph.D. (post-graduate) degree in a technical discipline such as Computer Science, Information Technology, Computer Engineering, or Electrical Engineering.<br> &nbsp;<br> &nbsp;Qualifications:<br> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proven ability to work with partners and drive collaboration.<br> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proven technical leadership skills: storage technologies and applications, Windows Storage Server, software development.<br> 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience configuring computer systems and managing networks.<br> 4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Effective troubleshooting skills.<br> 5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Strong written and verbal communication skills.<br> 6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ability to research technical issues and generate creative/innovative solutions.<br> 7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proven ability to deliver multi-person/multi-site, complex, hardware/software products and to help the team develop requirements, designs, schedule estimates, and test plans that will enable successful project<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; execution.<br> 8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Demonstrable programming skills in C and/or C++, as well as scripting.<br> 9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Software development, object-oriented design and/or software test knowledge.<br> 10.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Self directed, highly motivated, strong work ethic.<br> &nbsp;<br> Desired qualifications:<br> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Understanding of computer architecture.<br> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experience with Linux or HP-UX operating systems.<br> &nbsp; <img src="http://ars2.equest.com/?response_id=ab194e971f0d8484eda9bcc6f621f819&amp;view" alt=" " width=1 height=1></div><a id=jt_return_to_search_2 class=jt_return_to_search href="/c2/search.cfm?site%5Fid=1#job7431951">&laquo;&nbsp;Return to Results</a></div></td></tr></table><iframe src="/c/includes/jvi.cfm?site_id=1&job=7431951" style=display:none;width:1px;height:1px;></iframe></div></td></tr></table></div><div id=jt_footer> Copyright &copy; 2007 JobTarget, All Rights Reserved.<br><a href=http://www.jobtargetjobfinder.com>Job Seeker Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtarget.com/corp/products-services/job-board-solutions/ >Job Board Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtargetoneclick.com>Recruiting Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=/c2/tou.cfm>Terms of Usage</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtarget.com/corp/privacy-policy/ >Privacy Policy</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtarget.com/corp/company/company-overview/ >About JobTarget</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/c2/support.cfm?site_id=1">Contact JobTarget</a></div></body></html><div id=overDiv style="position: absolute; display: none; z-index: 1000;"></div>

