													$('jt_map_enlarge').show();">Smaller map</a><a id=jt_map_street_zoom href=javascript:void(0); onclick=map.setZoom(15);>Zoom to Street</a><br><br><div id=jt_map style="width: 99%; height: 200px; border: 1px solid black;"></div></div></div></div><div id=jt_job_summary><p><em>This is not an entry-level position.</em></p><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><th>Job ID:</th><td>7267223</td></tr><tr><th>Job Duration:</th><td>Indefinite</td></tr><tr><th>Position Title:</th><td>Intermediate Developer - Mobile Clients</td></tr><tr><th>Required Travel:</th><td>0-10%</td></tr><tr><th>Min Education:</th><td>BA/BS/Undergraduate</td></tr></table></td><td><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><th>Posted:</th><td>October 7, 2010</td></tr><tr><th>Industry:</th><td>Computer Software</td></tr><tr><th>Job Function:</th><td>Research</td></tr><tr><th>Min Experience:</th><td>1-2 Years</td></tr><tr><th>Job Type:</th><td>Full-Time</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></div><div id=jt_job_contact><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><th>Contact Person:</th><td>Claire Toplis</td></tr><tr><th>Email Address:</th><td id=jt_job_email><script language=javascript type=text/javascript>protectMail("ctoplis", "truecontext.com");</script></td></tr></table></td><td><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><th>Phone:</th><td>613-599-8288 Ext. 2118</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></div><div id=jt_job_description><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><strong><span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">TrueContext Intermediate Developer &ndash; Mobile Clients</span></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"><strong><span>Position Description</span></strong><span>:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;">Join a team that is shaping the way businesses use the mobile internet.&nbsp; We build software that makes mobile business a reality.&nbsp; TrueContext is a team of experts developing and delivering the next generation of software and services for the mobile internet.</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Our research and development team seeks a device software developer who is passionate about:</span></span></span></p><ul><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Software architecture and object-oriented design</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Writing clean, readable code</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Following best practices in software development and testing</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Leveraging the best of open source frameworks and APIs to solve common problems (IoC, MVC, ORM, etc)</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Automating the software production process</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Focusing in on the features that make our products exceptional</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Using agile methods for product design, planning, development, testing, and support</span></span></span></li></ul><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><strong><span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">SKILLS</span></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Ideally, you have qualifications or experience in multiple of the following:</span></span></span></p><ul><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Software development for mobile devices using native APIs (iPhone, Blackberry, Android, Windows Mobile, Symbian)</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Software development using mobile device frameworks like PhoneGap and Rhomobile</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Software development for web applications (server side and web clients) using Java and Ruby</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Software development for mobile devices using Objective-C, J2ME, .Net CF, C/C#</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Software development using user interface technologies and APIs (JavaScript, iUI, jQTouch, jQuery, DOJO, HTML, CSS)</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Implementation of open source APIs and libraries which implement common design patterns</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Integration with enterprise systems (relational DBs, LDAP, messaging systems)</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Use of cloud computing platforms and services (AWS, Google)</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Use of IDEs and tools for software development (JIRA, Eclipse, Subversion, Ant, Maven, Cruise Control)</span></span></span></li><li><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Use of testing tools (Selenium, JMeter)</span></span></span></li></ul><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><strong><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: small;">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p><br><b>Job Requirements</b><br><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><strong><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Position Qualifications and Personal Traits: </span></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Software Engineering or Computer Science degree or equivalent work experience is preferred.</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">The ideal candidate is a motivated, hardworking and a creative thinker who is effective in either a team or independent environment. He or she should have excellent communication and problem solving skills. Given our rapidly changing environment, the successful candidate will have an ability to comprehend and adapt quickly to new situations and technologies.&nbsp; They should be able to demonstrate initiative, flexibility and leadership skills.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">This is a development position to be located in the TrueContext Ottawa office.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><strong><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Interested?</span></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span style="color: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: small;">Please send your resume in confidence to </span><a href=mailto:jobs@truecontext.com><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: small;">jobs@truecontext.com</span></a><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">. </span></span></span></p></div><a id=jt_return_to_search_2 class=jt_return_to_search href="/c2/search.cfm?site%5Fid=1#job7267223">&laquo;&nbsp;Return to Results</a></div></td></tr></table><iframe src="/c/includes/jvi.cfm?site_id=1&job=7267223" style=display:none;width:1px;height:1px;></iframe></div></td></tr></table></div><div id=jt_footer> Copyright &copy; 2007 JobTarget, All Rights Reserved.<br><a href=http://www.jobtargetjobfinder.com>Job Seeker Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtarget.com/corp/products-services/job-board-solutions/ >Job Board Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=http://www.jobtargetoneclick.com>Recruiting Services</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=/c2/tou.cfm>Terms of Usage</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=