_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEmploymentTypeKey class=bodybold>Employment type</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEmploymentType class=body>Full Time</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEducationKey class=bodybold>Education</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEducation class=body>Bachelor</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblYearExperienceKey class=bodybold>Year Experience</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblYearExperience class=body>3 - 4 Years of Practical Experience</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblTravelKey class=bodybold>Travel</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblTravel class=body>Not Specified</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblCreateDateKey class=bodybold>Published on</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblCreateDate class=body>11/22/2010</span></td></tr></table><table width=385 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=10 valign=top><tr><td class=headerJobDetails><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblDescriptionKey>Description</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblDescription class=body>PLANIT Technology Group is currently recruiting a direct hire Web Dissemination Manager for our client located in Dulles, Virginia.<br>The successful candidate will manage the day to day operations and projects for the Web Dissemination team. Coordinate with other departments to prioritize business needs and requirements. Guide software architecture, design, development and testing activities. Mentor and coach development team members. Run Scrum meetings and resolve project challenges.<br>Manage on-going project risks. Coordinate with different departments and teams to make sure projects are on time and within budget. <br><br>Position Responsibilities Include:<br>*Consult with customer concerning requirements and/or maintenance of software system. <br>*Review and document system requirements and modifications to support e-commerce B2B solutions, middleware services, COTS implementations.<br>*Determine feasibility of design within time and cost constraints.<br>*Prepare detailed design specifications from which solutions can be built.<br>*Involved in application design, development and testing activities<br>*Manage day to day operations and projects<br>*Must have exceptional oral and written communication skills with the ability to converse with a broad spectrum of personnel.<br>*Occasional travel may be required.<br><br>Experience & Technical Skill Set Required:<br>*Eight years or more of related experience is preferred. Experiences in running enterprise level web developments desired.<br>*Familiar with Software Development Life Cycle and different software development methodologies and processes desired.<br>*Familiar with SOA is a plus.<br>*Programming background with experience or familiarity with the following: C#, XML, SOAP, ASP.NET, SQL, Web Services, Java and JavaScript technologies.<br>*Databases: SQL Server and Oracle.<br>*Software Design: UML, Use Case, Process Modeling, Rational Unified Process (RUP) is a plus. <br>*Operating Systems: Windows and Linux. <br>*Infrastructure Software: Application Servers, Web Servers, Middleware products and developing Web application.<br><br>Education Requirements:<br>Bachelors Degree in Computer Science, Engineering or equivalent field.<br><br>Work Status & Clearance Requirements:<br>US Citizenship & Secret Security Clearance Required.<br><br><br>For consideration, please submit your resume today! Visit us at www.planittech.com<br><br>PLANIT Technology Group<br>18310 Montgomery Village Ave., Suite 460<br>Gaithersburg, MD 20879<br>Main: (301) 987-1293<br>Fax: (301) 987-1296<br><br>PLANIT Technology Group, headquartered in Virginia Beach, VA, is a premier provider of information technology services, infrastructure and business solutions to a broad range of commercial clients within the United States. PLANIT is an EOE.df-tc</span><br><br><br><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperienceKey>Experience/Skills</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperience class=body>Web Dissemination, C#, XML,SOAP,ASP.NET,Java,Web Services,SQL Server Database, Oracle Database,Linux, Application Servers, Web Servers, COTS Implementation,Software Development Life Cycle,UML,Use Case,Process Modeling, Rational Unified Process, RUP, Scrum</span><br></td></tr></table><!-- google_ad_section_end --></td></tr><tr id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_trBottom><td valign=middle align=center height=50><input type=image name=ctl00$ctl00$contentMaster$content$btnApplyJobBottom id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_btnApplyJobBottom title="Apply to this job" src=/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_off.jpg onclick="location.href = 'http://www.tech-centric.net/Candidate/ApplyJob.aspx?JobID=733482'; return false;" onmouseover="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_on.jpg'" onmouseout="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_off.jpg'" border=0></td></tr></table></div></td><!--end center col--><!--begin right col--><td align=right valign=top width=120><table width=120 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td valign=middle><div id=tooltop><table width=120 height=27 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td><div align=center><img id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_Tools1_imgToolsTitle title=Tools src=/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/title_tools.jpg height=16 width=39 border=0></div></td></tr></table></div></td></tr><tr><td><div id=toolbox><table width=120 height=254 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td align=center><a id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_Tools1_hhlCreateResume title="Tech Computer IT Technology Resume" href=/Candidate/Resume.aspx style=display:inline-block;><img title="Tech Computer IT Technology Resume" onmouseover="this.src = '/App_