<td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEmploymentTypeKey class=bodybold>Employment type</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEmploymentType class=body>0-3 Month Contract</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEducationKey class=bodybold>Education</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEducation class=body>Not Specified</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblYearExperienceKey class=bodybold>Year Experience</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblYearExperience class=body>1 - 2 Years of Practical Experience</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblTravelKey class=bodybold>Travel</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblTravel class=body>None</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblCreateDateKey class=bodybold>Published on</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblCreateDate class=body>11/22/2010</span></td></tr></table><table width=385 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=10 valign=top><tr><td class=headerJobDetails><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblDescriptionKey>Description</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblDescription class=body>Unison Systems is looking for eperienced Access (VBA) Developers for a short-term project working from our client's location in downtown Denver. Our client, a Finanical Services company specializing in loan "due diligence" and asset management services, requires assistance in adding enhancements to an existing internal application. This is an internal underwriting database that runs a series of tests againsts client loans to ensure underwriting accuracy and compliance. This underwriting database is made up of a VBA front end (Access 2010) and SQL backend (using "Active Data Objects" for Access). Candidate(s) will be working onsite under the direction of client's internal software subject-matter-expert to develop additional internal loan due diligence tests for the underwriting database.<br><br>MUST HAVE:<br><br> - 2-3+ years of VBA development experience<br><br> - Basic SQL skills (basic SQL Query writing skills are a must)<br><br> - Any experience/understanding of loan underwriting process/financial acumen<br>C# (not required, but will help a great deal)<br><br>Location: Denver, CO<br><br>Duration: 2-3 months<br><br>Unison Systems Inc. is a full-service IT consulting firm that specializes in both IT contingency based staffing and end-to-end IT Business and Software solutions. As an independent, locally owned consulting firm that has been in business since 1997, we have 3 main areas of expertise: Software Life Cycle Support, Data Warehouse Support, and Infrastructure Support.df-tc</span><br><br><br><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperienceKey>Experience/Skills</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperience class=body>SQL,VBA,,</span><br></td></tr></table><!-- google_ad_section_end --></td></tr><tr id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_trBottom><td valign=middle align=center height=50><input type=image name=ctl00$ctl00$contentMaster$content$btnApplyJobBottom id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_btnApplyJobBottom title="Apply to this job" src=/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_off.jpg onclick="location.href = 'http://www.tech-centric.net/Candidate/ApplyJob.aspx?JobID=733573'; return false;" onmouseover="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_on.jpg'" onmouseout="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_off.jpg'" border=0></td></tr></table></div></td><!--end center col--><!--begin right col--><td align=right valign=top width=120><table width=120 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td valign=middle><div id=tooltop><table width=120 height=27 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td><div align=center><img id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_Tools1_imgToolsTitle tit