ntentMaster_content_lblEmploymentTypeKey class=bodybold>Employment type</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEmploymentType class=body>Full Time</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEducationKey class=bodybold>Education</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEducation class=body>Not Specified</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblYearExperienceKey class=bodybold>Year Experience</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblYearExperience class=body>4 - 5 Years of Practical Experience</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblTravelKey class=bodybold>Travel</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblTravel class=body>Not Specified</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblCreateDateKey class=bodybold>Published on</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblCreateDate class=body>12/3/2010</span></td></tr></table><table width=385 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=10 valign=top><tr><td class=headerJobDetails><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblDescriptionKey>Description</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblDescription class=body><b>No third party submittals</b><br><b>US citizen or permanent resident only.</b><br><br><b>Position Description:</b><br><br>Help in design and build business critical web applications using all of Microsoft's technologies. Lead a team of developers that reacts quickly to the needs of a fast paced business. Need a lead developer that takes initiative and is self motivated. <br><br><b>Responsibilities:</b><br><ul><li>Build scalable enterprise solutions <li>Provide technical support for ongoing initiatives <li>Integrate emerging technologies with Legacy systems <li>Analyze Client's business processes, focusing on optimizing existing capabilities <li>Recommend and design technical improvements to maximize productivity and data exploitation & management <li>Drive projects from conceptualization through to successful deployment in an operational environment <li>Leverage software development expertise to provide support to improve the performance of ongoing initiatives <li>Excellent written and oral communication skills <li>Excellent teamwork and leadership skills <li>Other duties as assigned.<br></ul><br><p><b><u>Required Skills, Knowledge and Experience:</u></b></p><ul><li>4+ years of.Net coding experience <li>3+ years of C#.Net <li>Extensive experience in developing ASP.NET applications using Visual Studio 2010 Team System <li>Strong SQL Server 2005 database skills <li>Coding experience with.Net 2.0 and 3.5 frameworks <li>Knowledge of.NET software design principles - OOD and UML including experience with software development methodologies (eg Agile, RUP) <li>UI experience - Infragistics, Telerik Rad <li>Unit testing experience - N Unit, MSUnit <li>Mocking framework - exposure to Rhino mocks, NUnitMocks <li>Experience interfacing with current database technologies <li>Strong practical knowledge/experience with Object-oriented programming (OOP) <li>Experience with lifecycle development and architecture of enterprise level applications with relational or XML based storage solutions <li>Proficiency with Microsoft Office suite of products. <li>Bachelors Degree <li>Experience of managing and developing staff. </ul><p><b><u>Preferred Skills, Knowledge and Experience:</u></b></p><ul><li>Oracle database and/or applications integration experience as a plus <li>Experience working with Onshore/Off-shore environment is desirable </ul><p>Email your resume with ' <b>910-1001 Senior.Net Developer </b>" in the subject line to (see below) </p><br>df-tc</span><br><br><br><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperienceKey>Experience/Skills</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperience class=body></span><br></td></tr></table><!-- google_ad_section_end --