 be able to develop high quality code. <br><br><strong>Required skills</strong></p><ul><li>Flex - minimum of 2 years - must have some hands on Flex 4 work <li>AS3 - 2+ Years <li>OO Development experience. </li></ul><p><strong>Preferred Skills:</strong></p><ul><li>XML Data Feeds <li>SOAP and REST Web Services</li></ul>df-tc</span><br><br><br><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperienceKey>Experience/Skills</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperience class=body></span><br></td></tr></table><!-- google_ad_section_end --></td></tr><tr id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_trBottom><td valign=middle align=center height=50><input type=image name=ctl00$ctl00$contentMaster$content$btnApplyJobBottom id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_btnApplyJobBottom title="Apply to this job" src=/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_off.jpg onclick="location.href = 'http://www.tech-centric.net/Candidate/ApplyJob.aspx?JobID=735769'; return false;" onmouseover="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_on.jpg'" onmouseout="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_off.jpg'" border=0></td></tr></table></div></td><!--end center col--><!--begin right col--><td align=right valign=top width=120><table width=120 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td valign=middle><div id=tooltop><table width=120 height=27 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td><div align=center><img id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_Tools1_imgToolsTitle title=Tools src=/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/title_tools.jpg height=16 width=39 border=0></div></td></tr></table></div></td></tr><tr><td><div id=toolbox><table width=120 height=254 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td align=center><a id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_Tools1_hhlCreateResume title="Tech Computer IT Technology Resume" href=/Candidate/Resume.aspx style=display:inline-block;><img title="Tech Computer IT Technology Resume" onmouseover="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_createre