ter_content_lblEmploymentTypeKey class=bodybold>Employment type</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEmploymentType class=body>Full Time</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEducationKey class=bodybold>Education</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblEducation class=body>Not Specified</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblYearExperienceKey class=bodybold>Year Experience</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblYearExperience class=body>4 - 5 Years of Practical Experience</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblTravelKey class=bodybold>Travel</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblTravel class=body>Not Specified</span></td></tr><tr><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblCreateDateKey class=bodybold>Published on</span></td><td><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblCreateDate class=body>12/5/2010</span></td></tr></table><table width=385 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=10 valign=top><tr><td class=headerJobDetails><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblDescriptionKey>Description</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblDescription class=body><p>Local Candidates Only ...<br>MUST be US Citizen or Green Card Holder ... <br><br><strong><u>SYSTEMS ENGINEER (VMware)</u></strong></p><p>This company is an exciting, high-growth company. This year the Atlanta Business Chronicle ranked them # 10 fastest-growing company in Atlanta. The company have also been ranked as high as #10 on the INC 500 list of fastest-growing private companies in the country. <br>The company offers rewarding, one-of-a-kind opportunities to individuals who thrive on entrepreneurial challenges. Located along the perimeter, north of Atlanta, it is a high-energy work environment filled with terrific people.</p><p><strong>Position Overview:</strong><br>We are looking for a dynamic individual interested in joining a customer focused IT team. Strong background in VMware technologies such as VMware ESX, VMware Virtual Center, VMware View, various VPN products, Storage administration and VDI backup and disaster recovery solutions.<br><br>Prefer a Candidates CERTIFIED in VMWARE (VCP, VCAP or VCDX)<br><br><strong>Required Skills: </strong><br>7+ years IT, and 5+ years virtualization experience required.<br>Hands-on experience with vSphere 4 and ESXi.<br>Experience with building and maintaining high-availability (>99%) environments.<br>Experience in virtualization VDI architecture using VMware technologies such as VMware ESX, VMware Virtual <br>Center, VMware View (View Manager, View Administrator, View Composer, View Client, and View Connection <br>Server).<br>A customer-service attitude and ability to work closely DEV and QA departments for testing.<br>Must be able to grasp the problems quickly and apply their experience for problem resolution and provide recommendations.<br>VMware and Virtual/Datacenter architecture is a must.<br>Strong hands-on experience with VMware VSphere supporting 20 or <br>more VMware Hosts.<br>Strong experience with SAN, NAS, EMC, and other storage products.<br>Proven experience (2-3 years) and knowledge of design, installation,<br>and configuration of Data Center <br>systems, protocols, and standards in Virtualization.<br>Performs end-to-end system administration of Windows server and<br>storage infrastructure. <br>Plans and deploys architectural improvements. <br>Manages shared system resources and collaborates with technical<br>staff throughout the company. <br>Translates Business and Project Team Requirements.<br>Performs advanced solution design including server and disk space<br>provisioning.<br>Performs System troubleshooting and backups.<br>Performs server maintenance and system upgrades including service packs, patches, and hot fixes. <br>Monitoring system resource utilization, trending, and capacity<br>planning. <br>7 years experience as a system administrator.<br>Experience in a MS Windows Server environment 2003/2008.<br>Experience with Active Directory, Microsoft networking (DNS, DHCP),<br>Exchange 2007/2010 server, and general network troubleshooting. <br>Experience with Citrix Presentation Server/XenApp as well as VDI <br>technologies.<br>Experience with Storage Area Networks (SANS).<br>Experience with Load Balancing technologies is a plus.<br>Experience with Microsoft Systems Center Operations Manager is a plus.</p>df-tc</span><br><br><br><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperienceKey>Experience/Skills</span><br><span id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_lblExperience class=body></span><br></td></tr></table><!-- google_ad_section_end --></td></tr><tr id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_trBottom><td valign=middle align=center height=50><input type=image name=ctl00$ctl00$contentMaster$content$btnApplyJobBottom id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_content_btnApplyJobBottom title="Apply to this job" src=/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_off.jpg onclick="location.href = 'http://www.tech-centric.net/Candidate/ApplyJob.aspx?JobID=735767'; return false;" onmouseover="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_on.jpg'" onmouseout="this.src = '/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/btn_applynow_off.jpg'" border=0></td></tr></table></div></td><!--end center col--><!--begin right col--><td align=right valign=top width=120><table width=120 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td valign=middle><div id=tooltop><table width=120 height=27 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td><div align=center><img id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_Tools1_imgToolsTitle title=Tools src=/App_Themes/PublicSite/Images/title_tools.jpg height=16 width=39 border=0></div></td></tr></table></div></td></tr><tr><td><div id=toolbox><table width=120 height=254 border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td align=center><a id=ctl00_ctl00_contentMaster_Tools1_hhlCreateResume title="Tech Computer 