cer teams. We support a large group of business users who care greatly about the application and user interface. Candidate should have a collaborative teamwork approach, strong work ethic and communication skills, and should expect to work directly with business users in sales, trading, and finance. <br> The current development team is split between London and New York with a 24x6 second line support team based in Singapore. The candidate should be prepare for global travel, primarily to London.<br><br><br><br> Main Duties<br><br> ? Assist with the design and development of sales reporting portals and other web based sales analytics applications for Equities using Flex, Java and J2EE frameworks <br><br> ? Handle the database development required for the sales portals<br> ? Drive full project life cycle until delivery and provide 3rd level of support for the application there after<br> ? Interface with other IT applications to collect and analyze requirements and deliver solutions<br> ? Deliver projects in fast-paced environment and work with different technology and business groups to produce quality and timely solutions.<br> ? Provide level 3 support for the sales applications<br> ? Continually stay aware of market trends to identify and apply new innovations for commercial results<br><br> Person Requirements<br><br> Requirements<br> Must have:<br> ? Excellent knowledge and experience in Flex and Java<br> ? Java Script, DHTML, AJAX<br> ? Three or more of the following skills : SharePoint, BI dashboards with any product (e.g. Cognos, Business Objects), Office Add-Ins, SilverLight, WPF, WinForms, ASP.NET, Flex, ExtJS<br> ? The ability to be ?technology ambidextrous? ? quickly being productive in other similar languages/environments<br> ? User interface design & implementation experience<br> ? SQL experience <br> ? Experience with agile development<br> ? Collaborative team-work approach, good work ethics<br> ? Good analytical skills and creative thinking skills, quick learner<br> ? Energetic and motivated, willing to take on challenging tasks, work independently and take on time pressure<br> ? Communication and organization skills<br><br> Nice to have:<br> ? Spring and other framework knowledge<br> ? Ant<br> ? OLAP understanding <br> ? Experience working in capital markets <br><br><br><br> Go to http://www.cmp.jobs to see more jobs.</font><br><p><font class=attribute><b>Experience Level:</b></font><br><font class=text>Unspecified</font><br><p><font class=attribute><b>Requirements:</b></font><br><font class=text></font><br></td></tr><tr><td align=left valign=top width=305><p><font class=attribute><b>Location:</b></font><br><font class=text>New York NY</font><br><p><font class=attribute><b>Duration:</b></font><br><font class=text>Direct Placement</font><br><p><font class=attribute><b>Pay Rate:</b></font><br><font class=text>$75/h</font><br></td><td width=405 align=right valign=center><table width=405 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td align=right class=blueborder bgcolor=E7EFF7><table width=405 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 border=0><tr><td colspan=4 bgcolor=FFFFFF align=center><font class=attribute style="font-size:10pt ; line-height:1.4em"><b>Similar Jobs</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width=4%>&nbsp;</td><td width=15% nowrap align=left><a class=joblinks href=http://www.net-temps.com/job/huwk/11-00762/java_developer.html>Jersey City, NJ</a></td><td width=3%>&nbsp;</td><td width=78% align=left><a class=joblinks href=http://www.net-temps.com/job/huwk/11-00762/java_developer.html>Java Developer</a></td></tr><tr><td width=4%>&nbsp;</td><td width=15% nowrap align=left><a class=joblinks href=http://www.net-temps.com/job/k2xz/14359jg/asp_net_c_sql.html>New York, NY</a></td><td width=3%>&nbsp;</td><td width=78% align=left><a class=joblinks href=http://www.net-temps.com/job/k2xz/14359jg/asp_net_c_sql.html>ASP.Net, C#, Sql Server, Junior</a></td></tr><tr><td width=4%>&nbsp;</td><td width=15% nowrap align=left><a class=joblinks href=http://www