jobwrapper><div id=jobsummary><div id=jobsummary_content><h2>Job Summary</h2><dl><dt>Company</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Sasken Network Solutions Inc</span></dd><dt>Location</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Plano, TX 75075</span></dd><dt>Industries</dt><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Telecommunications Services</span></dd><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Computer Software</span></dd><dd class=multipleddlast><span class=wrappable>Computer/IT Services</span></dd><dt>Job Type</dt><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Part Time</span></dd><dd class=multipleddlast><span class=wrappable> Temporary/Contract/Project</span></dd><dt>Years of Experience</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>1+ to 2 Years</span></dd><dt>Education Level</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Bachelor's Degree</span></dd><dt>Career Level</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Experienced (Non-Manager)</span></dd></dl></div></div><div id=jobcopy><h1>Field Test Engineers / Mobile Testing</h1><h2>About the Job</h2><div id=jobBodyContent><span id=TrackingJobBody name=TrackingJobBody><ul style="MARGIN-TOP: 0in" type=disc><li class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; COLOR: navy; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Roles & Responsibilities:&nbsp;&nbsp; <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></span></li></ul><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 1in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1"><span style="COLOR: #262626; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">ü<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Perform Field Test, Customer Acceptance Test and Operator Supports on 2G/3G/HSPA/DVBH mobile terminals.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 1in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1"><span style="COLOR: #262626; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">ü<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Perform the testing activities in network operators & vendor laboratories if needed.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 1in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1"><span style="COLOR: #262626; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">ü<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Collect, analyze and compile FT results and log files and deliver these to project teams and Error Data Base.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 1in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1"><span style="COLOR: #262626; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">ü<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Raise issues with accurate description, issues retest, ad-hoc issues retest in the correct environment and deliver accurate feedback to the project for the same.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 1in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1"><span style="COLOR: #262626; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">ü<spa