in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style="MARGIN-TOP: 0in" type=disc><li class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; COLOR: navy; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Skill set requirement : <o:p></o:p></span></li></ul><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 1in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 1in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1"><span style="COLOR: #262626; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">ü<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Candidate should be from Mobile Testing (Protocol and Application Testing) background.</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 1in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1"><span style="COLOR: #262626; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">ü<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Experience in Android, Windows Mobile, EMP and ODM platform will be an added advantage.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 1in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1"><span style="COLOR: #262626; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">ü<span style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>