        </script><!-- End Demdex Tag Insertion Manager --><div id=monsterAppliesPageWrapperCover></div><div id=monsterAppliesPageWrapper><!-- mnsNav --><div id=monsterAppliesHeaderHolder><div id=mAH_top><div id=monsterAppliesHeaderHolder_Overflow><a href=http://www.monster.com id=logo_monster_apply alt=Jobs title=Jobs><span>Monster Home</span></a><div class=mainMenuHeader><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderLeft><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderLeftTop></div><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderLeftBottom></div></div><div class=mainMenuHeaderCentral><div class=mainMenuHeaderCenterTop><ul><li class=mAH_firstLi><a href=http://www.monster.com>Home</a></li><li><a href=http://my.monster.com>Profile & Resume</a></li><li><a href=http://jobsearch.monster.com>Jobs</a></li><li><a href=http://my.monster.com/Career-Management/Landing.aspx>Career Tools</a></li><li><a href=http://career-advice.monster.com>Advice</a></li><li><a href=http://my.monster.com/communities/default.aspx>Communities</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderRight><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderRightTop></div><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderRightBottom></div></div></div></div></div><div class=monsterAppliesHeaderHolder_minWidth></div></div><!-- ltlJobBodyContent --><div id=monsterAppliesContentHolder><div id=monsterheader xmlns><img src=http://media.newjobs.com/jobview_standard/images/monster.gif alt=Monster width=115 height=19></div><div id=outerwrapper xmlns><div id=bodycol><div id=jobheadertop>&#160;</div><div id=jobheader><img border=0 src=http://media.monster.com/xw88774410wx/joblogo.gif alt="Sensus Metering Systems" id=companyLogo class=logo onerror=removeLogo()><p id=companyNameHeader style=display:none>Sensus USA-Conservation Solutions</p><div id=subicons><img src=http://media.newjobs.com/jobview_standard/images/pixel.gif height=1 width=1 alt style=margin:0px></div><div style=clear:both;height:1px>&#160;</div><div id=jobheaderbottom>&#160;</div></div><div id=jobwrappertop2>&#160;</div><div id=jobwrapper><div id=jobsummary><div id=jobsummary_content><h2>Job Summary</h2><dl><dt>Company</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Sensus USA-Conservation Solutions</span></dd><dt>Location</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Atlanta, GA 30301</span></dd><dt>Industries</dt><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Energy and Utilities</span></dd><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Computer/IT Services</span></dd><dd class=multipleddlast><span class=wrappable>Engineering Services</span></dd><dt>Job Type</dt><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Full Time</span></dd><dd class=multipleddlast><span class=wrappable> Employee</span></dd><dt>Career Level</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Experienced (Non-Manager)</span></dd><dt>Job Reference Code</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>356</span></dd></dl></div></div><div id=jobcopy><h1>Project Manager</h1><h2>About the Job</h2><div id=jobBodyContent><span id=TrackingJobBody name=TrackingJobBody><font id=TrackingJobBody name=TrackingJobBody face=Arial><p><font xmlns=http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml><font size=3><b>Sensus USA is seeks a highly talented Project Manager.​ <a class=exLink href=http://www.sensus.com/WhySensus.xml>Our technologies enable the intelligent use and conservation of water and energy, improve operations and reduce environmental impact.​ </a>&nbsp;Visit <a href=http://www.sensus.com/ class=exLink>www.​sensus.​com</a> to learn more about us.​ </b><i><b><br></b></i></font></font></p></font><font face=Arial><br></font><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3><br>Project Manager will be responsible for effective&nbsp; management of assigned projects and project teams to successfully complete each project, on-time, on-budget and within specification. The ultimate goal is to achieve total customer satisfaction.<br></font><p class=MsoNormal><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>&nbsp;</font></p><p class=MsoNormal><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3><b>Job Responsibilities</b></font></p><p class=MsoNormal><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>The PM must have experience with installation of large projects at a customer site. The key factors/experience needed are coordinating manufacture of a product and delivery to the customer site according to an installation schedule that is created with/by the customer. Customer coordination skills and system acceptance experience are necessary</font></p><p class=MsoNormal><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3><br></font></p><p class=MsoNormal><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>&nbsp;</font></p><p><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3><p class=MsoNormal><font xmlns=http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml><b>Job Requirements:. </b></font></p><font xmlns=http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml></font></font><font face=Arial size=3><p class=MsoNormal><font xmlns=http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml>&nbsp;</font></p><font xmlns=http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml></font></font><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3></font></p><ul><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Bachelor's degree in a technical discipline. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>8+ years of project management experience. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Utility market experience a plus. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Knowledge of RF Networking and installation.</font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Project management experience in coordination of all aspects of a project including client relations, developing project budgets and scopes of work, schedule development and leading a project team. Experience in leading and coordinating all phases of project development both internal and external to Sensus. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Demonstrated ability to determine key business issues and develop appropriate action plans from multi-disciplinary perspectives. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Effective leadership, project management, and consulting skills. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Excellent verbal, written and interpersonal communication skills. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>The PM must have experience with installation of large projects at a customer site. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>The key factors/experience needed are coordinating manufacture of a product and delivery to the customer site according to an installation schedule that is created with/by the customer. </font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Customer coordination skills and system acceptance experience are necessary</font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>Must be available for up to 50% travel however will not be weekly and this is a work from home role. <br></font></li><li><font style="font-size: small;" face=Arial size=3>PMP certification preferred</font></li></ul><br>Click here to apply:<br><a href="http://tbe.taleo.net/NA5/ats/careers/requisition.jsp?org=SENSUS&cws=1&rid=328" target=_blank><a href="http://tbe.taleo.net/NA5/ats/careers/requisition.jsp?org=SENSUS&cws=1&rid=356">http://tbe.taleo.net/NA5/ats/careers/requisition.jsp?org=SENSUS&cws=1&rid=356</a></a><br><br>Or click "Apply" below<br></span><img src=http://media.newjobs.com/jobview_standard/images/pixel.gif height=1 width=1 alt style=margin:0px></div></div></div><div id=bodycolbottom>&#160;</div></div><div id=sidecol><div class=sidecolboxtop>&#160;</div><div class=sidecolbox id=jobtools><h2>Job Tools</h2><ul><li class=apply><a mns_rt=Apply href="javascript:openPanel('HIDE');">Apply</a></li><li class=print><a href=javascript:window.print() mns_rt=Print>Print</a></li><li class=save><a href="http://my.monster.com/JobFile/JobFile.aspx?jobid=91339617&action=ADD&fjs=1&jobtitle=Project+Manager" mns_rt=SaveToFile>Save</a></li><li class=share><a href="
