        </script><!-- End Demdex Tag Insertion Manager --><div id=monsterAppliesPageWrapperCover></div><div id=monsterAppliesPageWrapper><!-- mnsNav --><div id=monsterAppliesHeaderHolder><div id=mAH_top><div id=monsterAppliesHeaderHolder_Overflow><a href=http://www.monster.com id=logo_monster_apply alt=Jobs title=Jobs><span>Monster Home</span></a><div class=mainMenuHeader><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderLeft><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderLeftTop></div><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderLeftBottom></div></div><div class=mainMenuHeaderCentral><div class=mainMenuHeaderCenterTop><ul><li class=mAH_firstLi><a href=http://www.monster.com>Home</a></li><li><a href=http://my.monster.com>Profile & Resume</a></li><li><a href=http://jobsearch.monster.com>Jobs</a></li><li><a href=http://my.monster.com/Career-Management/Landing.aspx>Career Tools</a></li><li><a href=http://career-advice.monster.com>Advice</a></li><li><a href=http://my.monster.com/communities/default.aspx>Communities</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderRight><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderRightTop></div><div class=mainMenuHeaderBorderRightBottom></div></div></div></div></div><div class=monsterAppliesHeaderHolder_minWidth></div></div><!-- ltlJobBodyContent --><div id=monsterAppliesContentHolder><div id=monsterheader xmlns><img src=http://media.newjobs.com/jobview_standard/images/monster.gif alt=Monster width=115 height=19></div><div id=outerwrapper xmlns><div id=bodycol><div id=jobheadertop>&#160;</div><div id=jobheader><img border=0 src=http://media.monster.com/xitrgroupx/joblogo.gif alt="ITR Group" id=companyLogo class=logo onerror=removeLogo()><p id=companyNameHeader style=display:none>ITR Group</p><div id=subicons><img src=http://media.newjobs.com/jobview_standard/images/pixel.gif height=1 width=1 alt style=margin:0px></div><div style=clear:both;height:1px>&#160;</div><div id=jobheaderbottom>&#160;</div></div><div id=jobwrappertop2>&#160;</div><div id=jobwrapper><div id=jobsummary><div id=jobsummary_content><h2>Job Summary</h2><dl><dt>Company</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>ITR Group</span></dd><dt>Location</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Minneapolis, MN</span></dd><dt>Job Type</dt><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Full Time</span></dd><dd class=multipleddlast><span class=wrappable> Temporary/Contract/Project</span></dd></dl></div></div><div id=jobcopy><h1>Front End Web Engineer - Web Developer</h1><h2>About the Job</h2><div id=jobBodyContent><span id=TrackingJobBody name=TrackingJobBody><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" face="'Georgia','serif'">&nbsp;</p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Front End Web Engineers to help build innovative, responsive and scalable online consumer facing website.<br></font></font><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri><br>The qualified candidate will have expertise of client-side programming techniques and tools, and also be keenly aware of server-side (i.e. JSP or PHP) development best practices. The ability to hand-code elegant and standards-compliant HTML 5, CSS and object oriented JavaScript is required, as is deep knowledge of front-end engineering issues that affect the user experience, such as page performance, SEO, browser compatibility and accessibility. The engineer will work in a fast paced, collaborative and fun team environment with both technical and non-technical staff, so demonstrated communication and teamwork skills are critical.<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><o:p><font face=Calibri>&nbsp;</font></o:p></font></b></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font face=Calibri><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt">Minimum Job Qualifications</font></b><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt">:<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>BS in Computer Science OR equivalent experience<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>At least 5 years of industry experience building mid to large scale consumer facing web applications<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Well versed in front-end performance optimization and tools<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Strong background in web application development using HTML 5, CSS, Object-oriented Javascript, jQuery, JSP/PHP<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Experience using 3<sup>rd</sup> party developer APIs<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><o:p><font face=Calibri>&nbsp;</font></o:p></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font face=Calibri><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt">Preferred Job Qualifications</font></b><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt">:<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Familiarity with software lifecycle and development tools such as Subversion, Jira or Basecamp <o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Extended knowledge of UI frameworks or technologies such as YUI, EXTJS, Flex/Flash, etc. <o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Strong presentation skills and the ability to transfer complex knowledge to others<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Experience developing mobile (native or web) applications<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Active contributor to open standards or the development community<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt"><font face=Calibri>Intellectual breadth, beyond software<o:p></o:p></font></font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal></font><font style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><o:p></o:p></font>&nbsp;</p><div id=jdpRequirements class="jdpContent stdInnerContent"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We are unable to provide sponsorship at this time and only considering local candidates. If you meet these qualifications, all inquiries will be responded to within 24 hours. Thank you. <br><br>The ITR Group is one of the premier consulting and staffing firms in the Twin Cities. We specialize in contract, contract for hire and permanent opportunities for technical skill sets. For more information check out our website at <a class=exLink href=http://www.itrgroupinc.com/ jquery1286203563036=3 exlinkattribute=http://www.itrgroupinc.com%2f><font color=#3366cc><a href=http://www.itrgroupinc.com>http://www.itrgroupinc.com</a> /</font></a><br><br>ITR Group is an Equal Opportunity Employer</p></div></span><img src=http://media.newjobs.com/jobview_standard/images/pixel.gif height=1 width=1 alt style=margin:0px></div></div></div><div id=bodycolbottom>&#160;</div></div><div id=sidecol><div class=sidecolboxtop>&#160;</div><div class=sidecolbox id=jobtools><h2>Job Tools</h2><ul><li class=apply><a mns_rt=Apply href="javascript:openPanel('HIDE');">Apply</a></li><li class=print><a href=javascript:window.print() mns_rt=Print>Print</a></li><li class=save><a href="http://my.monster.com/JobFile/JobFile.aspx?jobid=91212691&action=ADD&fjs=1&jobtitle=Front+End+Web+Engineer+-+Web+Developer" mns_rt=SaveToFile>Save</a></li><li class=share><a href="
