><h2>Job Summary</h2><dl><dt>Company</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>AboutWeb</span></dd><dt>Location</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Gaithersburg, MD 20899</span></dd><dt>Industries</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Staffing/Employment Agencies</span></dd><dt>Job Type</dt><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Full Time</span></dd><dd class=multipleddlast><span class=wrappable> Employee</span></dd><dt>Years of Experience</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>2+ to 5 Years</span></dd><dt>Education Level</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Bachelor's Degree</span></dd></dl></div></div><div id=jobcopy><h1>Senior SharePoint Developer</h1><h2>About the Job</h2><div id=jobBodyContent><span id=TrackingJobBody name=TrackingJobBody><font color=black face="'Times New Roman','serif'"><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 19.2pt; MARGIN: 0in 0in 11.25pt 0.5in; BACKGROUND: white" class=MsoNormal><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; COLOR: #555555; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">We are looking for a candidate to join our Sharepoint practice. The initial project involves working with our client in Gaithersburg on site to enhance and add addditonal finctionality, create workflows and help create input for the optimal settings for the SharePoint Server. Sharepoint 2007, WSS and MOSS. This will be a multi-faceted position which will include supporting the servers, developing the portal interfaces, collaborating with our client’s internal developers and helping them understand and work effectively with their new system. You will also be working with the upper management to give them some higher level insight into how to fully utilize, to whatever extent possible, the Sharepoint system.&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>Duties:<br>*Provide technology subject matter expertise to our client’s development and infrastructure teams. *Develop, maintain and improve operational procedures supporting the portal and collaboration implementation*Provide hands-on training to various users and groups on the use and support of the portal system*Help to develop corporate standards *Perform on-going process/technology improvements to satisfy end user needs*Communicate with managers and the organization on issues, new technology, upgrades, new releases, issue resolution and potential risks such as incompatibility with other tools. Experience:<br>3+ years with Windows SharePoint as well as Microsoft .Net frameworks including C# and asp.net, 3+ years experience with Microsoft Office SharePoint Server 2007 and Windows SharePoint Services; 3+ years of SharePoint Designer 2007 experience preferred; 3+ years experience with SQL Server 2000, Experience using Microsoft .Net frameworks to customize and leverage Windows SharePoint services is a must.<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 19.2pt; MARGIN: 0in 0in 11.25pt 0.5in; BACKGROUND: white" class=MsoNormal><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; COLOR: #555555; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">Interested candidates please contact Sarah Schauffler at <a href=mailto:sschauffler@aboutweb.com><a href="mailto:sschauffler@aboutweb.com?subject=Senior%20SharePoint%20Developer">sschauffler@aboutweb.com</a></a> or (301) 468-9246 X104 <br>No Third Party Please<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt" class=MsoNormal></font>&nbsp;</p></span><img src=http://media.newjobs.com/jobview_standard/images/pixel.gif height=1 width=1 alt style=margin:0px></div></div></div><div id=bodycolbottom>&#160;</div></div><div id=sidecol><div class=sidecolboxtop>&#160;</div><div class=sidecolbox id=jobtools><h2>Job Tools</h2><ul><li class=apply><a mns_rt=Apply href="javascript:openPanel('HIDE');">Apply</a></li><li class=print><a href=javascript:window.print() mns_rt=Print>Print</a></li><li class=save><a href="http://my.monster.com/JobFile/JobFile.aspx?jobid=86725289&action=ADD&fjs=1&jobtitle=Senior+SharePoint+Developer" mns_rt=SaveToFile>Save</a></li><li class=share><a href="
