div></div><div id=jobwrappertop2>&#160;</div><div id=jobwrapper><div id=jobsummary><div id=jobsummary_content><h2>Job Summary</h2><dl><dt>Company</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Picerne Real Estate Group</span></dd><dt>Location</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Warwick, RI 02886</span></dd><dt>Industries</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Real Estate/Property Management</span></dd><dt>Job Type</dt><dd class=multipledd><span class=wrappable>Full Time</span></dd><dd class=multipleddlast><span class=wrappable> Employee</span></dd><dt>Years of Experience</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>5+ to 7 Years</span></dd><dt>Education Level</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Bachelor's Degree</span></dd><dt>Career Level</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>Experienced (Non-Manager)</span></dd><dt>Job Reference Code</dt><dd><span class=wrappable>IT</span></dd></dl></div></div><div id=jobcopy><h1>Network Administrator</h1><h2>About the Job</h2><div id=jobBodyContent><span id=TrackingJobBody name=TrackingJobBody><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Picerne Real Estate Group, a national real estate owner/apartment manager has an exciting opportunity for&nbsp;an individual seeking a career as&nbsp;a&nbsp;Network Administrator.<br></font><p><font face=Tahoma size=3></font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3></font></p></font><p><font face=Tahoma size=3></font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3></font></p><p class=Objective style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><font face=Tahoma size=3><u><br>Job Function</u><br>The candidate will be responsible for the company’s Microsoft Windows-based network and general end-user support. The position has responsibility for maintenance, upgrades and support to all server, desktop and technology operations for the Northeast Region, including the corporate office and remote sites.&nbsp; The candidate will coordinate with and provide additional support as needed to the Florida and Arizona regions. </font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><u></u><br><font face=Tahoma size=3>The Network Administrator is responsible for supporting the company’s network. This position includes installing, configuring and maintaining all network hardware and software. <br><u><br>Duties and Responsibilities</u><br>Sense of urgency to resolve issues independently</font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Strong oral and written communication skills <br>Strong customer (internal) focus <br>Planning and organizational skills <br>Ability to work on multiple projects <br>Self motivated and directed <br>Analytical and problem-solving capabilities procedures </font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Vendor management Picerne Real Estate Group, Rhode Island’s largest full service Real Estate </font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Office communication and other technical systems</font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3></font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size=3><font face=Tahoma><font style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><br></font><u>Technical Skills</u><br>Windows Server 2003 & Active Directory</font></font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Microsoft Exchange Server 2003 </font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Working knowledge of PC / Server / Network / Printer hardware </font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Knowledge of DENS, WINS, DACAPO, TCP/IP & networking protocols<br>Yardi Property Management Software </font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Advanced knowledge of Microsoft Office products <br>Experience with <font class=RadEWrongWord id=RadESpellError_5>Veritas</font> Backup (or comparable backup solution) <br>Understanding of Network topology <br>Basic understanding of Cisco Routers and Switches </font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>SQL 2000</font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3></font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size=3><font face=Tahoma><font style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><br></font><u>Experience and Education</u><br>At least 5 years of hands-on IT experience in a Microsoft Windows environment and degree in Computer Science. <br><br></font></font></p><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face=Tahoma size=3>Picerne Real Estate Group is an equal opportunity Employer.</font></p></span><img src=http://media.newjobs.com/jobview_standard/images/pixel.gif height=1 width=1 alt style=margin:0px></div></div></div><div id=bodycolbottom>&#160;</div></div><div id=sidecol><div class=sidecolboxtop>&#160;</div><div class=sidecolbox id=jobtools><h2>Job Tools</h2><ul><li class=apply><a mns_rt=Apply href="javascript:openPanel('HIDE');">Apply</a></li><li class=print><a href=javascript:window.print() mns_rt=Print>Print</a></li><li class=save><a href="http://my.monster.com/JobFile/JobFile.aspx?jobid=94479206&action=ADD&fjs=1&jobtitle=Network+Administrator" mns_rt=SaveToFile>Save</a></li><li class=share><a href="
    http://jobsearch.monster.com/emailfriend.aspx?JobID=94479206&JobLocation=Warwick%2c+RI+02886&JobTitle=Network+Administrator&CompanyName=Picerne+Real+Estate+Group&redirect=http%3a%2f%2fjobsearch.monster.com%2f
  " mns_rt=EmailFriend>Share</a></li></ul></div><div class=sidecolboxtop>&#160;</div><div class=sidecolbox id=companytools><h2>Company Tools</h2><ul><li><a href="http://jobsearch.monster.com/Search.aspx?co=xw25920177wx" mns_rt=Jobs>View all Jobs at this Company</a></li><li><a href=http://company.monster.com/profiles/picerne-real-estate-group.aspx target=blank mns_rt=companyprofileclick>View Company Profile</a></li></ul></div></div></div><p/><p/></div><form id=forApply><input type=hidden id=atp name=atp value=2><input type=hidden id=cstrd name=cstrd value=4481><input type=hidden id=jobCategory name=jobCategory value=660><input type=hidden id=jobOccupation name=jobOccupation value=660.11882><input type=hidden id=jobTitle name=jobTitle value="Network Administrator, Picerne Real Estate Group, Warwick, RI 02886"><input type=hidden id=jobPosition name=jobPosition value="Network Administrator"><input type=hidden id=jobLocation name=jobLocation value="Warwick, RI 02886"><input type=hidden id=jobCompany name=jobCompany value="Picerne Real Estate Group"><input type=hidden id=jobID name=jobID value=94479206><input type=hidden id=jobCountryID name=jobCountryID value=0><input type=hidden id=linkBack name=linkBack value=http%3a%2f%2fjobsearch.monster.com%2f><input type=hidden id=applyUrl name=applyUrl value=http%3a%2f%2fmy.monster.com%2fapplyStart.asp%3fjobid%3d94479206%26redirect%3dhttp%253a%252f%252fjobsearch.monster.com%252f><input type=hidden id=jobCountry name=jobCountry value><input type=hidden id=jobRefCode name=jobRefCode value><input type=hidden id=jobBoardID name=jobBoardID value><input type=hidden id=reuID name=reuID value><input type=hidden id=disclaimerID name=disclaimerID value><input type=hidden id=caurlID name=caurlID value></form><div id=monsterAppliesPageWrapperWhiteSpace></div></div><!-- ucFooter--><script type=text/javascript>
