iguration, development and testing skills.&nbsp;Basic Qualifications:A Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent experience with a major or minor in computer science or related field A minimum of 3 years of experience with Kana Connect and/or Brick Street. Specialized experience in programming or database languages and techniques for application systems design.Strong communication, project management, analytical, and leadership skills.Strong interpersonal, verbal &amp; written communication skills.Skills Preferred:Java/J2EE: Solaris, Unix and Shell Scripting: Oracle/DB2/SQL: WebsphereTCP/IP, HTTP, POP, SMTP, SMPPDNS, LDAP, MQ, NDM, FTP, TelnetHTML, XML, XSLT, Java ScriptKnowledge of spam and e-mail/SMS technologies/processes and CRM toolsVendor and product management.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<p><p>Please refer to job code <b>10-03467</b> when responding to this ad.<p><table><tr><td><b>Category:</b></td><td>Information Technology</td></tr><tr><td></td><td> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;>&nbsp;<a target=_blank href="/public/csearch.mpl?search_string=TEC63%20or%20Programmer%20or%20Programm%2A&search_method=boolean&search_radius=&search_zip_code=&industry_code=TEC&chk_search_radius=&reward=&start=&len=50&job_length=&search_scope=1">Programmer</a><br></td></tr><tr><td><b>Location:</b></td><td>Mettawa, IL</td></tr><tr><td><b>County:</b></td><td>Lake County</td></tr><tr><td><b>ZIP Code:</b></td><td>60045</td></tr><tr><td><b>Pay Rate:</b></td><td>Open</td></tr><tr><td><b>Job Terms:</b></td><td>full time</td></tr><tr><td valign=top><b>Company:</b></td><td><a target=_blank href="/public/vrc.mpl?id=7364&utm_source=JobCircle&utm_medium=web&utm_campaign=classified_detail&utm_content=company_profile">Software Guidance</a></td></tr><tr><td><b>Phone:</b></td><td>914-366-5900 x5984</td></tr><tr><td><b>Fax:</b></td><td>email only</td></tr></table><form action=/public/require_login.mpl method=POST><input type=hidden value=6545456 name=id><input type=hidden value=8879 name=m><input type=hidd