fills the project objectives.<br>&nbsp; Assist on other projects as needed, perform other related duties and special projects as required.<br>&nbsp; Document flowcharting of proposed process and technology solutions.<br> Skills Required:&nbsp; 3-5 years mortgage experience.&nbsp; Evidence the ability to work with all levels of management.<br>&nbsp; Ability to multi-task more than one assigned project<br><p><p>Please refer to job code <b>10-04296</b> when responding to this ad.<p><table><tr><td><b>Category:</b></td><td>Information Technology</td></tr><tr><td></td><td> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;>&nbsp;<a target=_blank href="/public/csearch.mpl?search_string=TEC154%20or%20Business%20Process%20Analysis%20or%20business%20process%20and%20%28analysis%20or%20analyst%29&search_method=boolean&search_radius=&search_zip_code=&industry_code=TEC&chk_search_radius=&reward=&start=&len=50&job_length=&search_scope=1">Business Process Analysis</a><br></td></tr><tr><td><b>Location:</b></td><td>Columbus, OH</td></tr><tr><td><b>County:</b></td><td>Franklin County</td></tr><tr><td><b>ZIP Code:</b></td><td>43085</td></tr><tr><td><b>Pay Rate:</b></td><td>Open</td></tr><tr><td><b>Job Terms:</b></td><td>full time</td></tr><tr><td valign=top><b>Company:</b></td><td><a target=_blank href="/public/vrc.mpl?id=7364&utm_source=JobCircle&utm_medium=web&utm_campaign=classified_detail&utm_content=company_profile">Software Guidance</a></td></tr><tr><td><b>Phone:</b></td><td>914-366-5900 x5984</td></tr><tr><td><b>Fax:</b></td><td>email only</td></tr></table><form action=/public/require_login.mpl method=POST><input type=hidden value=7327545 name=id><input type=hidden value=8879 name=m><input type=hidden value=10%2D04296 name=c><input type=hidden value=jc name=partner><table width=410 border=0><tr><td valign=top align=right><input type=submit value="Apply to Job"></td></tr></table></form><!-- [ END CLASSIFIED DATA ] --></td></tr></table></td><td bgcolor=#ffffff><img src=/images/spacer.gif width=3></td