s/tweet_share.png width=31 height=27 alt="Bookmark and Share" style=border:0></a><script type=text/javascript src=http://s7.addthis.com/js/200/addthis_widget.js></script>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a onclick="window.open('/public/flag_content.mpl?cid=7218969','flag_content_window','menubar=no,width=500,height=400,toolbar=no,status=no,location=no');" onmouseover="window.status='Flag Content.'; return true;" onmouseout="window.status=''; return true;"><img src=/images/job_flag_content.gif border=0 title="Flag Content"></a><hr></td></tr></table><p><form action=/public/require_login.mpl method=POST><input type=hidden value=7218969 name=id><input type=hidden value=9396 name=m><input type=hidden value=CRR%2DSWEngineer7 name=c><input type=hidden value=jc name=partner><table width=410 border=0><tr><td valign=top align=right><input type=submit value="Apply to Job"></td></tr></table></form><h3>Telecommute Software Engineer - Java Developer -...</h3><i>Posted:&nbsp; December 6, 2010</i><br><p style="word-wrap:break-word; width:390">Telecommute Software Engineer - Java Developer - Programmer - OO Telecommute Software Engineer - Java Developer - Programmer - SQL - ERM - Systems - Skills Required - Java, SQL Database Development, Database Design, Entity-Relationship Modeling (ERM), Visual Builder Tools, Systems Experience<p> Software Engineer - Java Developer - Programmer - SQL - Database Developer - ERM - Systems<p>If you are a Software Engineer with extensive Java and SQL Database development/design experience, please read on!<p>**THIS IS A FULL-TIME (NOT CONTRACT) POSITION THAT WILL ALLOW 100% TELECOMMUTING.&nbsp; AN ACTIVE SECURITY CLEARANCE IS A PLUS BUT NOT REQUIRED**<p>This is an opportunity to fully utilize your Java and Database development experience with cutting edge technology.&nbsp; This is a position that will allow you to work on multiple projects across many commercial and government (military) business units.&nbsp; We are looking for 4 Software Developers to work on the development of our next-generation collaborative training system and 3D visualization frameworks.&nbsp; If you do not live in GA then working remotely is available.&nbsp; THIS IS NOT A CONTRACT POSITION.&nbsp; This position does require either an active security clearance or the ability to obtain a security clearance.<p>We are looking for 3+ years of experience with the following:<p>- Experience using frameworks in Java or a similar object-oriented language<br>- Deep understanding of SQL (DB Design) or entity-relationship modeling (ERM)<br>- Experience in Design Coding and Implementations.<br>- Solid grounding in software engineering tools<br>- Expert Systems experience<br>- Experience implementing applications with windowed user interfaces<br>- Experience using and/or designing visual builder tools<br>- Top Secret Clearance preferred; Secret Clearance required.&nbsp; <p>What youll be doing:<p>- Development of our next-generation collaborative training system and 3D visualization frameworks.<br>- Systems Development<br>- Java Development<br>- SQL Database Design and modeling<br>- Using and/or designing visual builder tools.<p>Whats in it for you:<p>- Excellent compensation<br>- Excellent benefits<br>- Working on multiple cross-functional projects <p>So, if you are a Software Engineer with extensive Java and SQL Database development/design experience, please apply today! - CRR-SWEngineer7 - , , , , ,&nbsp; CyberCoders&nbsp; CyberScientific <p>Job ID: CRR-SWEngineer7<br><p><p>Please refer to job code <b>CRR-SWEngineer7</b> when responding to this ad.<p><table><tr><td><b>Category:</b></td><td>Information Technology</td></tr><tr><td></td><td> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;>&nbsp;<a target=_blank href="/public/csearch.mpl?search_string=TEC60%20or%20General%20Computers%2FIT%20or%20Info%2A%20Tech%2A%20or%20Co