ross Product Technology to resolve issues and refine requirements. Candidate will adhere to design and development standards to produce high quality software .Candidate must have ability to work in a dynamic paced environment and also provide second level production support.<br><br>Qualifications<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10+ years experience<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Bachelor's degree in computer science or engineering<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Strong in database (Sybase, SQL Server 2000 or above, Oracle)<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Strong Java Server-side software development (Java, J2EE, EJB, JSP, Servlets, JMS, Web Services, SOAP, WSDL, HTML, XML, XSL, JavaScript). <br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hands-on working knowledge with Java frameworks : Spring, Hibernate <br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Working Knowledge of Aqua logic BPM, TIBCO Tools (EMS )<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Unix and scripting skills<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ability and willingness to learn new technology and quickly grasp various applications and its functionality<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ability to interact with offshore team for development work<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Team Player<br><br>�&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Good communication skills<p>Please refer to job code <b>10-01617</b> when responding to this ad.<p><table><tr><td><b>Category:</b></td><td>Information Technology</td></tr><tr><td></td><td> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;>&nbsp;<a target=_blank href="/public/csearch.mpl?search_string=TEC776%20or%20Other%20Information%20Technology%20or%20Information%20Technology&search_method=boolean&search_radius=&search_zip_code=&industry_code=TEC&chk_search_radius=&reward=&start=&len=50&job_length=&search_scope=1">Other Information Technology</a><br></td></tr><tr><td><b>Location:</b></td><td>Warren, NJ</td></tr><tr><td><b>County:</b></td><td>Somerset County</td></tr><tr><td><b>ZIP Code:</b></td><td>07059</t