						addthis_brand = "Job.com";
						addthis_pub    = "vaweb2007";     
					</script><div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style" style="float:right; margin-top:5px;"><a class=addthis_button_facebook></a><a class=addthis_button_delicious></a><a class=addthis_button_email></a><a class=addthis_button_favorites></a><span class=addthis_separator>|</span><a href="http://addthis.com/bookmark.php?v=250&pub=vaweb2007" class=addthis_button_expanded>More</a></div><script type=text/javascript src="http://s7.addthis.com/js/250/addthis_widget.js#pub=vaweb2007"></script></div></div><h4 class=jobView_company><em>Company:</em> Capital Markets&nbsp;<br><span class=listLocation><em style=font-size:11px;>Location:</em> New York, New York </span></h4><ul id=jobSummary><li><em>Salary:</em> $150,000 &nbsp; - &nbsp; $150,000 </li><li><em>Category:</em> Information Tech / Computer</li><li><em>Date Posted:</em> 10/13/2010</li><li><em>Travel Required:</em> Not Specified</li><li><em>Security Clearance:</em> No</li><li><em>Work Type:</em> Any</li></ul><h4 class=insideTitle title="Job Description">Job Description</h4><blockquote class=insideBlock><p> The Quantitative Strategies team is a quantitative Portfolio Management Desk. The Desk manages one of the largest hedge funds in the world using sophisticated quantitative models. It trades across assets classes on a global basis using a wide variety of instruments (cash securities, futures, forwards, options, interest rate swaps and other OTC derivatives). <br><br>The QS Technology team works closely with the business providing a wide range of services. The technology group is expanding and require a programmer analyst with a quantitative background (typically a science orientated education), strong technology skills and a keen interest in supporting a fast moving, demanding and stimulating business. Technology supports the full breadth of the platform which the business uses. It spans a production statistical portfolio construction system, through to generating and executing orders in derivative instruments. <br><br>The rewards of this role include working with a first class team, learning the quantitative technology platform and working with the investment management process from construction to execution. <br><br>Principal Responsibilities: <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Work as part of the Research Technology team, reporting to the teams manager. <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Play a high profile role working side by side with the Portfolio Management team on research and production efforts. <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Specialize in the the core research and portfolio construction system Plutus. <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Implement technology solutions for complex business problems. The problems could be mathematical in nature requiring a basic understanding of linear algebra, probability and statistics. <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Progress the technology to give horizontal scalability and Matlab integration <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Work across multiple software components and technologies, including C++, Sybase, VB and Java. <br><br>Core Skills <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; At least two years of experience in a technology role <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; C++ and database (ideally Sybase). Core skills sets will be vetted. <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Interfacing to data vendors, gathering and validating market data real time of interest but not essential. <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Exposure to and appreciation of Futures, Forward, IR Swap, Option or CDS contracts. <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cooperate within a team and work in a rigorous and stimulating environment <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ability to gather requirements and distill business analysis <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Strong commitment toward best practices within enterprise development and deployment <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ability to prototype and develop efficiently, test new software <br><br></p></blockquote><div id=applyLink align=center><a href="/my.job/search/page=applyjob/" title="Apply to Job" onclick rel=nofollow>Click here to apply now</a></div></div></div><div style=clear:both;><h3 class=freeModule_hdr>More jobs you may like:</h3><div class=resultsSubset><table width=100% class=resultsList border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 summary="Job.com View of JobSearch Records" style="clear: both;"><col width=60%><col width=40%><tr><td valign=top colspan=2 style=border-bottom:0;padding-top:8px;><div style=float:right;margin:3px;><h2 class=postDate_results title="Job Posted on 12/02">Post date: <em>12/02</em></h2></div><h2 class=jobTitle_results><a id=link70357731 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70357731/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Sr. PHP Developer">Sr. PHP Developer</a></h2><h4>Capital Markets</h4></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:8px;">New York, New York</td><td align=right style="padding-right:3px;white-space:nowrap;padding-right:10px;border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:8px;" width=40%><a id=link70357731 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70357731/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Sr. PHP Developer">View Job &raquo;</a></td></tr><tr><td valign=top colspan=2 style=border-bottom:0;padding-top:8px;><div style=float:right;margin:3px;><h2 class=postDate_results title="Job Posted on 12/01">Post date: <em>12/01</em></h2></div><h2 class=jobTitle_results><a id=link70196801 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70196801/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Principal Technical Architect">Principal Technical Architect</a></h2><h4>Capital Markets</h4></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:8px;">New York, New York</td><td align=right style="padding-right:3px;white-space:nowrap;padding-right:10px;border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:8px;" wi