						addthis_brand = "Job.com";
						addthis_pub    = "vaweb2007";     
					</script><div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style" style="float:right; margin-top:5px;"><a class=addthis_button_facebook></a><a class=addthis_button_delicious></a><a class=addthis_button_email></a><a class=addthis_button_favorites></a><span class=addthis_separator>|</span><a href="http://addthis.com/bookmark.php?v=250&pub=vaweb2007" class=addthis_button_expanded>More</a></div><script type=text/javascript src="http://s7.addthis.com/js/250/addthis_widget.js#pub=vaweb2007"></script></div></div><h4 class=jobView_company><em>Company:</em> Capital Markets&nbsp;<br><span class=listLocation><em style=font-size:11px;>Location:</em> New York, New York </span></h4><ul id=jobSummary><li><em>Salary:</em> $110,000 &nbsp; - &nbsp; $110,000 </li><li><em>Category:</em> Information Tech / Computer</li><li><em>Date Posted:</em> 11/17/2010</li><li><em>Travel Required:</em> Not Specified</li><li><em>Security Clearance:</em> No</li><li><em>Work Type:</em> Any</li></ul><h4 class=insideTitle title="Job Description">Job Description</h4><blockquote class=insideBlock><p><br><br>Job Description <br><br>For: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Information Architect <br><br>Location: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; New York, NY <br><br>Looking for a highly organized, proactive Information Architect with solid experience in IA development, product requirements analysis, UI documentation, prototyping and testing. The Information Architect will report directly to the Design Director and will work on public facing, intranet and extranet Web applications. A strong ability to work with multiple business owners and on multiple projects is a must. The Information Architect will: <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Collaborate with senior design staff and business owners on workflow, UI requirements, prototypes, use cases and user profiles <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ensure that functional requirements documents properly reflect a projects full page and screen inventory <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ensure that functional requirements document properly reflect each page or screens functionality <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Create, maintain and update reference UI wire frames for all pages and screens <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Create prototypes and help manage user testing <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Collaborate with senior design staff to insure proper execution of interaction design <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Collaborate with QA staff to insure proper implementation of features and functions <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Research, report on and test emerging interaction design methods and implementation technologies <br><br>Expected Background <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Bachelors degree or higher in Visual Design, Information Architecture, Cognitive Interaction, or related field <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3+ years of experience in business analysis and information architecture <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Experience with Azure and Fireworks <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Strong experience with design process <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Very strong detail and process orientation <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Experience in an e-commerce, media, or start-up environment with tight release cycles <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Intranet/extranet experience <br><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ability to follow set standards and drive projects through to completion <br><br>About the client: <br><br>Gerson Lehrman Group (GLG) provides technology and services to support a marketplace for expertise. Our web-based platform for consultation and collaboration enables our clients (750+ of the worlds leading financial services firms, consultancies, corporations, and nonprofits) to find, engage, and manage 175, 000+ experts in a broad range of industries and disciplines. <br><br>GLG has grown quickly since inception in 1998 and currently employs more than 600 people in 14 offices worldwide. Our diverse, energetic staff and innovative technologies enable us to successfully compete with much larger organizations. We are a privately held company with 2007 revenue in excess of $225 million. <br><br></p></blockquote><div id=applyLink align=center><a href="/my.job/search/page=applyjob/" title="Apply to Job" onclick rel=nofollow>Click here to apply now</a></div></div></div><div style=clear:both;><h3 class=freeModule_hdr>More jobs you may like:</h3><div class=resultsSubset><table width=100% class=resultsList border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 summary="Job.com View of JobSearch Records" style="clear: both;"><col width=60%><col width=40%><tr><td valign=top colspan=2 style=border-bottom:0;padding-top:8px;><div style=float:right;margin:3px;><h2 class=postDate_results title="Job Posted on 12/02">Post date: <em>12/02</em></h2></div><h2 class=jobTitle_results><a id=link70357731 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70357731/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Sr. PHP Developer">Sr. PHP Developer</a></h2><h4>Capital Markets</h4></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:8px;">New York, New York</td><td align=right style="padding-right:3px;white-space:nowrap;padding-right:10px;border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:8px;" width=40%><a id=link70357731 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70357731/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Sr. PHP Developer">View Job &raquo;</a></td></tr><tr><td valign=top colspan=2 style=border-bottom:0;padding-top:8px;><div style=float:right;margin:3px;><h2 class=postDate_results title="Job Posted on 12/01">Post date: <em>12/01</em></h2></div><h2 class=jobTitle_results><a id=link70196801 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70196801/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Principal Technical Architect">Princi