. Attention to detail <br><br>Excellent communication skills. Ability to work well under pressure. A solid understanding of HTML. Proficiency in the Microsoft Office suite of products. A strong working knowledge of Adobes products. Knowledgeable about trading software and trading industry terminology is a plus. Graphic design experience is a plus. A bachelors degree in technical writing or a related field <br></p></blockquote><div id=applyLink align=center><a href="/my.job/search/page=applyjob/" title="Apply to Job" onclick rel=nofollow>Click here to apply now</a></div></div></div><div style=clear:both;><h3 class=freeModule_hdr>More jobs you may like:</h3><div class=resultsSubset><table width=100% class=resultsList border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 summary="Job.com View of JobSearch Records" style="clear: both;"><col width=60%><col width=40%><tr><td valign=top colspan=2 style=border-bottom:0;padding-top:8px;><div style=float:right;margin:3px;><h2 class=postDate_results title="Job Posted on 12/02">Post date: <em>12/02</em></h2></div><h2 class=jobTitle_results><a id=link70357731 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70357731/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Sr. PHP Developer">Sr. PHP Developer</a></h2><h4>Capital Markets</h4></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:8px;">New York, New York</td><td align=right style="padding-right:3px;white-space:nowrap;padding-right:10px;border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;padding-bottom:8px;" width=40%><a id=link70357731 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70357731/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Sr. PHP Developer">View Job &raquo;</a></td></tr><tr><td valign=top colspan=2 style=border-bottom:0;padding-top:8px;><div style=float:right;margin:3px;><h2 class=postDate_results title="Job Posted on 12/01">Post date: <em>12/01</em></h2></div><h2 class=jobTitle_results><a id=link70196801 href="/my.job/search/page=jobview/key=70196801/" class=bold title="View the full ad for Principal Technical Arc