utilizing CDNs, e.g., Akamai<br>- Strong analytical, evaluation and problem-solving skills;<br>- Ability to effectively communicate with client and glean business requirements;<br>- Understanding of full lifecycle development for systems and software; <br>- Previous involvement in establishing, communicating, and applying development standards, effectively communicating methodologies, and guiding others in their application. </div><!-- end dc_content --></div><!-- end job_description --><div class=company_overview><h1>Company Overview</h1><div class=dc_content><h2><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=308&did=10364781&cn=SavvyConsulting+LLC">find more jobs with this company</a></h2><div style=clear:both;></div></div></div><!-- end company_overview --><dl class=buttons><dd class=save><a id=saveJob2 href=#; title="Save Job">Save this job</a></dd><dd class=email><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=305&dockey=xml/b/7/b7f25dd1d5eac0534ebc0abd5e1b29c9&source=null&ral=JobSearch?



