	  --><div id=description_col><dl class=buttons><dd class=save><a id=saveJob href=# title="Save Job">Save this job</a></dd><dd class=email><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=305&dockey=xml/8/6/86ef0f122d742be6b730fc02fd0d5285&source=null&ral=JobSearch?



					op=302







					%26dockey=xml/8/6/86ef0f122d742be6b730fc02fd0d5285">Email to a friend</a></dd><dt><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=318&dockey=xml/8/6/86ef0f122d742be6b730fc02fd0d5285&source=null&ral=JobSearch?



					op=302







					%26dockey=xml/8/6/86ef0f122d742be6b730fc02fd0d5285" target=_top>Click Here to Apply</a></dt></dl><div class=job_description><a class=printerFriendly href=# onclick="window.open('/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=302&printView=1&force=1&dockey=xml/8/6/86ef0f122d742be6b730fc02fd0d5285', 'PrintView', 'width=600, height=600, toolbar=0, scrollbars=1, menubar=0, location=0');">Printer-Friendly</a><h1>Job Description</h1><div class=dc_content><ul class=job_details><li class=position>Business Development Manager- IT Staffing</li><li class=location>New York, NY</li></ul> Business Development Manager (IT Staffing):<br><br>Damco Solutions, we are a global consulting and technology solutions & services company, offering industry-specific solutions on ERP, CRM, EAI and Data warehousing for domains like BFSI, Telecom, Public Sector and Utilities. Company with offices in USA, UK, Netherlands and ISO 9001:2000 certified offshore software development centers in New Delhi and Hyderabad, India. Since its inception in 1996, Damcosoft has honed its level of expertise in building bespoke applications, web applications, application integration, application re-engineering and migration, RFID, mobile and PDA solutions, ERP & CRM solutions. Our domain and technology experts have extensive experience of building and supporting business critical applications for our clients globally.We are currently looking for Business Development Managers for Damcosoft Inc in New York.<br><br>Responsibilities:<br><br>* Define and implement strategies that will help Damcosoft move up the value chain from staff augmentation to becoming a strategic solution provider to direct clients. * Build long-term relationships with direct clients and system integrators by meeting their IT Consulting resource needs and contributing to their growth. * Build excellent customer relationships at the C-level in the client organization. Understand the issues and challenges faced by the client executives and provide high level IT consulting to them, so they can see the value proposition of working with Damcosoft. * Develop and sustain effective new business relationships with accounts/clients and Independently handle staffing business & manage the team. * Decent understanding of technology concepts and its application. Should be able to evaluate technical skills reasonably. * Be conversant with the current advancements in technology and its usage from a business perspective * Ability to develop and sustain effective new business relationships with clients in order to leverage and set up effective commercial deals * Well aware of Recruitment life cycle and US Staffing * Strong communication skills both verbal and written. Good telephone comm. skills. Good listening skills. Good presentation skills, must be independent and a self-starter and have high risk taking capabilities.<br><br> Required Skills: * 7 to12 Years of experience in Business Development, US Staffing and Recruitment * Bachelors Degree, preferably Marketing however not mandatory. * New Business Development and account management * Top Management / Client facing capabilities * Proven Track Record in Business development * Team Handling capabilities * Well versed with IT/Technology<br><br> Desired Skills: * IT/software Certification. </div><!-- end dc_content --></div><!-- end job_description --><div class=company_overview><h1>Company Overview</h1><div class=dc_content><h2><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=308&did=10383634&cn=Damcosoft+Inc">find more jobs with this company</a></h2><div style=clear:both;></div></div></div><!-- end company_overview --><dl class=buttons><dd class=save><a id=saveJob2 href=#; title="Save Job">Save this job</a></dd><dd class=email><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=305&dockey=xml/8/6/86ef0f122d742be6b730fc02fd0d5285&source=null&ral=JobSearch?



