	  --><div id=description_col><dl class=buttons><dd class=save><a id=saveJob href=# title="Save Job">Save this job</a></dd><dd class=email><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=305&dockey=xml/0/0/009540e8cb67c37bf66de6492be422b1&source=null&ral=JobSearch?



					op=302







					%26dockey=xml/0/0/009540e8cb67c37bf66de6492be422b1">Email to a friend</a></dd><dt><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=318&dockey=xml/0/0/009540e8cb67c37bf66de6492be422b1&source=null&ral=JobSearch?



					op=302







					%26dockey=xml/0/0/009540e8cb67c37bf66de6492be422b1" target=_top>Click Here to Apply</a></dt></dl><div class=job_description><a class=printerFriendly href=# onclick="window.open('/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=302&printView=1&force=1&dockey=xml/0/0/009540e8cb67c37bf66de6492be422b1', 'PrintView', 'width=600, height=600, toolbar=0, scrollbars=1, menubar=0, location=0');">Printer-Friendly</a><h1>Job Description</h1><div class=dc_content><ul class=job_details><li class=position>Systems Engineer-Windows, Storage & Virtualization a plus</li><li class=location>San Francisco, CA</li></ul> Sr Systems Engineer/ Solution Architect<br><br>We are a company with a reputation for quality, integrity and service. We are working with cutting edge technology and offer a fantastic working environment. Many of our employees have been with us for years.<br>We are seeking a highly skilled Solution Architect/Systems Engineer with an entrepreneurial spirit. This individual possesses a background in IT Infrastructure and consulting services. The ideal candidate is able to help our customers align technical solutions with business challenges. Partnering with our Sales and Professional Services Teams, you will be extremely customer focused and thrives on the idea of helping customers and providing solutions. <br><br>We are looking for someone with: <br><br>Natural affinity and enthusiasm for working directly with clients helping them solve problems<br>Passion for technology fed by ongoing hunger for new knowledge<br>Able to confidently drive problem solving conversations with clients<br>A self starter who will thrive taking initiative in an autonomous environment<br>A consultant confident in his or her ability to exceed 50% billable rate <br>Someone who puts team first <br><br>Job Responsibilities (include but not limited to): <br><br>The System Engineer/Architect will provide expertise in enterprise solution design and assume responsibility for expertise in his/her area as to best practices and industry trends that will serve our clients. Additional responsibilities include:<br>Building relationships and nurturing business partnerships that enable us to offer more value to clients while increasing revenue and profit.<br>Leading with an obsession for customer satisfaction that is addressed and measured constantly. Superior Customer Service and problem solving skills a must<br>Proven project management skills.<br>Experience working within a professional services field, or consulting experience, system engineer experience and/or deploying enterprise software solutions preferred.<br>Experience with three or more of the following: Enterprise Architecture, Virtualization, Networking, Security, Systems Management, , Enterprise Application integration, and server & SAN, storage infrastructure are critical for success.<br>Experience with IBM hardware is of high value.<br>Experience with x86 Architecture<br>Comfort and skills in presenting to a technical audience.<br><br>Desired Skill Sets:<br><br>Bachelor*s degree a minimum, post graduate work a plus. <br>6-10 years experience in a similar role working with clients and sales support. Specific skills with design, setup, installation and troubleshooting for the following technologies:<br>Intel/AMD Server architecture and solution design (x86 Architecture a must)<br>Server Virtualization * VMWare, Xen, etc. (setup, installation, troubleshooting)<br>Microsoft OS and applications <br>Linux<br>Storage architecture and solution design (SAN, iSCSI, etc)<br><br>Great benefits, entrepreneur type of environment, extreme amount of flexibility, work from home, this is a small-team atmosphere where each person is encouraged to make a difference! </div><!-- end dc_content --></div><!-- end job_description --><div class=company_overview><h1>Company Overview</h1><div class=dc_content><h2><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=308&did=10328807&cn=Confidential+Company">find more jobs with this company</a></h2><div style=clear:both;></div></div></div><!-- end company_overview --><dl class=buttons><dd class=save><a id=saveJob2 href=#; title="Save Job">Save this job</a></dd><dd class=email><a href="/jobsearch/servlet/JobSearch?op=305&dockey=xml/0/0/009540e8cb67c37bf66de6492be422b1&source=null&ral=JobSearch?



