ilable </td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Location:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobLocation0_cbhlMapJob class=BingMap rel=nofollow href="#lat=40.7516,lon=-73.9877,mapsize=small,thumbnailmap=False,streetlevel=False,maptoken="><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/JS/jobresults/mapit.gif id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobLocation0_imgMapIt alt="map it!">US-NY-New York</a><iframe id=iframeForInlineMap frameborder=0 scrolling=no style=display:none;></iframe><div id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobLocation0_pnlLoadingMap class=loadingMap style=display:none;><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/js/widgets/loading.gif id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobLocation0_imgLoadingMap class=imgLoadingMap><br> Loading Map... </div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 align=center><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobMap0_cbhlMapJob class=BingMap rel=nofollow href="#lat=40.7516,lon=-73.9877,mapsize=small,thumbnailmap=True,streetlevel=True,maptoken="></a><iframe id=iframeForInlineMap frameborder=0 scrolling=no style=display:none;></iframe><div id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobMap0_pnlLoadingMap class=loadingMap><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/js/widgets/loading.gif id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobMap0_imgLoadingMap class=imgLoadingMap><br> Loading Map... </div></td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav> </td><td valign=top>  </td></tr><!--End Job Overview Table--><!--Begin Contact Info Table--><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Contact: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>Aaron Landman </td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Phone: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>212-593-9797 </td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Email: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks><a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/ApplyStart.aspx?Job_DID=J8H7V364B6M05RL7S2X">Send Email Now</a></td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Fax: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>Not Available </td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>  </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks></td></tr><tr><td> </td></tr><tr><td> </td></tr></table><!--End Contact Info Table--></td></tr><tr><td style="padding-top:30px; padding-bottom:20px;"><!--$JobSkinImage04$--></td></tr></table></td><td valign=top><table width=480 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=20><tr><td><p class=header2>Company Overview</p><p align=justify>Infinity Consulting Solutions (ICS) matches talented professionals with positions at many of the world's leading companies. Our clients include Fortune 100 firms and innovative high tech startups, in industries as diverse as financial services, legal, telecom, television and publishing.<br><br> Whether you're in the market for a permanent position, contract work or a contract-to-hire opportunity, ICS is plugged into a network of hiring managers looking for candidates ready to take the next step in their careers. </p><a id=complinks href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/Companies/CompanyDetails.aspx?HHName=infinitycscom">Learn More about Infinity Consulting Solutions</a><br><a href=http://www.infinity-cs.com id=complinks>Visit Our Website</a><br><a href=http://www.infinity-cs.com/jobsearch.asp id=complinks>View Job Postings</a><br><a href=http://www.infinity-cs.com/register.asp id=complinks>Register With ICS</a><br><br><br><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td><span class=job_title>Lead C++ Developer</span></td><td align=right class=apply>   <a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/ApplyStart.aspx?Job_DID=J8H7V364B6M05RL7S2X" onclick="CB.AskInfoBox.tallyApplyNowClick('A7A6636NMKLZ8GKXK9V');" class=btnJobSkin title="Apply for this job now!">Apply Now</a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_cbhlJobFeedback rel=nofollow target=_blank href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/accessible/jobfeedback.aspx?Job_DID=J8H7V364B6M05RL7S2X">Report It</a></span></td></tr></table><p class=header>Job Description </p><div class=job_desc><div class=RichText_Content><p>A world leading financial institution in equity trading and financial products is seeking a talented software developer to join their global team. The company executes over $200 billion in trading volume on average each day and has executed over 11 million trades with total volume surpassing $160 trillion since its inception. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><br><br><p class=header>Job Requirements </p><div class=job_req><div class=RichText_Content><p><b>Description of position:</b></p><p>Senior-level developer, most time spent hands-on coding with medium supervision, working as part of a small team, good communication skills necessary to coordinate development with team leader.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><b>Background:</b></p><p>Financial exchange; tel com; </p><p><b> </b>&nbsp;</p><p><b>Responsibilities/accountabilities:</b></p><p>Deliver high-quality applications, multiple releases, own unit testing</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><b>Skills:</b></p><p>Required:</p><p>•          Senior-level developer with 5-7 years of experience</p><p>•          Strong C++, experience </p><p>•          Experience with high throughput, low latency applications.</p><p>•          Experience in working with multi-threads, STL &amp; Design Patterns</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Pluses:</p><p>•          Server side development experience is preferred.</p><p>•          XML programming </p><p>•          Basic knowledge of network communication (TCP/IP protocol).</p><p>•          Basic knowledge of SQL</p><p>•          Basic knowledge of financial instruments</p></div></div><p> </p><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td> </td><td align=right class=apply>   <a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/ApplyStart.aspx?Job_DID=J8H7V364B6M05RL7S2X" onclick="CB.AskInfoBox.tallyApplyNowClick('A7A6636NMKLZ8GKXK9V');" class=btnJobSkin title="Apply for this job now!">Apply Now</a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_cbhlJobFeedback rel=nofollow target=_blank href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/accessible/jobfeedback.aspx?Job_DID=J8H7V364B6M05RL7S2X">Report It</a></span></td></tr></table><br><br><div class=jd_jobprivacy style="border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 3px 3px 0px; margin-left: 10px;"><font style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; color: #000000;"><strong>CareerBuilder.com's Advice</strong></font><br><br><table id=_JobDetailsv2_tblPrivacyBox border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tbody><tr valign=top><td valign=top width=30><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/JS/Icons/lock.gif></td><td valign=top><span id=privacy>For your<a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/Info/Privacy.htm?sc_cmp1=js_jobdetails_privacy"> privacy and protection</a>, when applying to a job online:<br>Never give your social security number to a prospective employer, provide credit card or bank account information, or perform any sort of monetary transaction. &nbsp;<a href=/JobSeeker/Info/Privacy.aspx style="color: #336666;">Learn More<span style="text-decoration: none;">&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</span></a><br><br>By applying to a job using CareerBuilder.com you are agreeing to comply with and be subject to the CareerBuilder.com<a href=http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/info/hhterms.htm> Terms and Conditions</a> for use of our website. To use our website, you must agree with the <a href=http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/info/hhterms.htm> Terms and 