mail: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks><a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/ApplyStart.aspx?Job_DID=J8E28T74LXF05WH0VK3">Send Email Now</a></td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Fax: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>Not Available </td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav></td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 height=30></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 align=center><a href="http://www.facebook.com/login.php?return_session=1&nochrome=1&fbconnect=1&extern=2&display=popup&api_key=f6d86738c854c6aeb0c5023c23548c4a&v=1.0&next=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.careerbuilder.com%2FJobSeeker%2FFacebook%2Fxd_receiver.htm%3Ffb_login%26fname%3D_opener%26guid%3D0.6778329019489395&cancel_url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.careerbuilder.com%2FJobSeeker%2FFacebook%2Fxd_receiver.htm%23fname%3D_opener%26%257B%2522t%2522%253A3%252C%2522h%2522%253A%2522fbCancelLogin%2522%252C%2522sid%2522%253A%25220.183%2522%257D&channel_url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.careerbuilder.com%2FJobSeeker%2FFacebook%2Fxd_receiver.htm&locale=en_US"><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/MediaManagement/95/MNA8H97325M5422ZN95.gif border=0></a><br></td></tr></table><!--End Contact Info Table--></td></tr><tr><td style="padding-top:30px; padding-bottom:20px;"><!--$JobSkinImage04$--></td></tr></table></td><td valign=top><table width=480 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=20><tr><td><p class=header2>Company Overview </p><p class=comp_over><center><!-- Start of Brightcove Player --><div style=display:none></div><!--

By use of this code snippet, I agree to the Brightcove Publisher T and C

found at http://corp.brightcove.com/legal/terms_publisher.cfm.

--><script language=JavaScript type=text/javascript src=http://admin.brightcove.com/js/BrightcoveExperiences.js></script><object id=myExperience61636820001 class=BrightcoveExperience><param name=bgcolor value=#FFFFFF><param name=width value=400><param name=height value=300><param name=playerID value=60836891001><param name=publisherID value=19582128001><param name=isVid value=true><param name=isUI value=true><param name=@videoPlayer value=61636820001></object><!-- End of Brightcove Player --></center><br><br><strong>Surrex Solutions Corporation</strong> is an Information Technology Consulting services provider specializing in Project Staffing, Software Development, Project Management, Contract Programming, Information Technology Staffing and Direct Hire for mid-size and Fortune 500 Companies. Surrex Consulting Service(s) Managers and Recruiters possess extensive technical and recruiting experience resulting in our ability to understand client requirements and supply the needed consulting resources.<br><br> We fulfill our promises with speed, quality and value to both our Consultants and our Clients. Our management team averages 20 years of direct information technology consulting industry experience. This extensive experience combined with reputations of excellence and professionalism provides clients with the utmost confidence in Surrex Solutions service offerings. Surrex strives for a mutually beneficial relationship, delivering to needs requirements, by which the Customer is in complete control of outcomes. </p><a id=complinks href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/Companies/CompanyDetails.aspx?HHName=SurrexSolutions123">Learn More about Surrex Solutions Corporation</a><br><a href=http://www.surrex.com/index.html id=complinks>Visit Our Website</a><br><br><br><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td><span class=job_title>C# ASP.NET Developer</span></td><td align=right class=apply><a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/AOReviewReq.aspx?Job_DID=J8E28T74LXF05WH0VK3" border=0><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/MediaManagement/3R/Mwp5RV69HHNT3WLK83R.gif vspace=2 border=0></a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_cbhlJobFeedback rel=nofollow target=_blank href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/accessible/jobfeedback.aspx?Job_DID=J8E28T74LXF05WH0VK3">Report It</a></span></td></tr></table><p class=header>Job Description </p><div class=job_desc><div class=RichText_Content><p><b>Position Summary:</b></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Responsible for development and support of Web Service, ASP.NET, ASP and SQL Server application development.  Additionally the position requires development and support for the clients core application Episys.</p></div> </div><br><br><p class=header>Job Requirements </p><div class=job_req><div class=RichText_Content><p><b>Technical Skills:</b></p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>* Eight or more years experience in software design and development using current technologies (.NET, Java, Oracle, etc.)</p><p>* Five or more years developing in a Microsoft/.NET environment (C# language preferred)</p><p>* Five or more years experience developing databases, stored procedures and TSQL in SQL Server (2005 or above preferred)</p><p>* Experience developing web services in Microsoft .NET</p><p>* Experience with web technologies such as HTML, XML, and Javascript</p><p>* Experience with Visual Sourcesafe and Visual Studio (2003 or later)</p><p>* Core banking or credit union development experience a plus</p><p>* Development and support of any enterprise class application environment a plus</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p><b>Personal Attributes:</b></p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>* Must have excellent written and oral communication skills</p><p>* Must be a self-starter capable of working directly with business units and coordinating instructions into definitive requirements</p><p>* Ability to balance development and support duties</p><p>* Understanding of formal development processes and methodologies</p><p>* Ability to design, develop and implement efficient solutions with little guidance</p><p>* Ability to work both individually and in a team environment</p><p>* Ability to learn technologies quickly with little or no formal training</p><p>* Ability to provide after hours support on rotational on-call schedule when needed</p><p>* Strong customer service skills</p><p>* Ability to estimate work effort and adhere to project timelines</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p><b>Other Skills and Experience:</b></p><p>* Four year degree or equivalent experience</p><p>* Finance/Banking experience a plus</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div> </div><p> </p><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td></td><td align=right class=apply><a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/AOReviewReq.aspx?Job_DID=J8E28T74LXF05WH0VK3" border=0><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/MediaManagement/3R/Mwp5RV69HHNT3WLK83R.gif vspace=2 border=0></a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_cbhlJobFeedback rel=nofollow target=_blank href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/accessible/jobfeedback.aspx?Job_DID=J8E28T74LXF05WH0VK3">Report It</a></span></td></tr></table><br><br><div class=jd_jobprivacy style="border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 3px 3px 0px; margin-left: 10px;"><font style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; color: #000000;"><strong>CareerBuilder.com's Advice</strong></font><br><br><table id=_JobDetailsv2_tblPrivacyBox border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tbody><tr valign=top><td valign=top width=30><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/JS/Icons/lock.gif></td><t