_desc><br><div class=RichText_Content><div><div><div><p><strong><a exlinkattribute=https://cls7.bullhornstaffing.com%2fBullhornStaffing%2fJobPosting%2fJobPosting.cfm%3fjobPostingID%3d1255%26noLogo%3dTRUE class=exLink href="https://cls7.bullhornstaffing.com/BullhornStaffing/JobPosting/JobPosting.cfm?jobPostingID=1255&noLogo=TRUE">Front-End Application Engineers </a></strong></p><div><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Design and deliver innovative solutions to provide high quality, bandwidth efficient video delivery</li><li>Expand Ooyala's product offering in the areas of content management, monetization, and syndication</li><li>Create user-interaction models that deliver an engaging video viewing experience</li><li>Expose cutting-edge Machine Learning and Computer Vision algorithms via elegant user interfaces</li></ul><p><strong><br></strong>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></div> </div><br><br><p class=header>Job Requirements </p><div class=job_req><div class=RichText_Content><span><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Passion for building products used by millions worldwide</li><li>BS/MS/PhD in Computer Science or equivalent from top tier school</li><li>2+ years of software development experience</li><li>Excellent programming skills -- experience with ActionScript, Javascript, Java, C++ or Ruby a plus</li><li>Experience with large scale consumer facing products, distributed systems a plus</li><li>Strong analytical and communication skills</li></ul></span></div> </div><p> </p><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td> </td><td align=right class=apply>   <a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/ApplyStart.aspx?Job_DID=J7X8G466F284P8DT8DK" onclick="CB.AskInfoBox.tallyApplyNowClick('AQ23G6BDDQYV1SKC65');" class=btnJobSkin title="Apply for this job now!">Apply Now</a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSk