 Now</a></td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Fax: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>Not Available </td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>  </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks></td></tr><tr><td> </td></tr><tr><td> </td></tr></table><!--End Contact Info Table--></td></tr><tr><td style="padding-top:30px; padding-bottom:20px;"><!--$JobSkinImage04$--></td></tr></table></td><td valign=top><table width=480 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=20><tr><td><p class=header>Company Overview </p><p class=comp_over align=justify><span class=style1>CareerPlanners, Inc.</span> provides information technology recruiting services to businesses and the Public Sector throughout the United States. CareerPlanners is a veteran-owned business that is totally committed to serving the IC (Intelligence Community). As innovators with a command of business and technical knowledge, CareerPlanners can help their clients identify hard-to-find candidates faster. Our technology expertise include: Application/Solution Development, SOA (Service Oriented Architecture), IT Portfolio Management/PMO, Middleware, Sales and Sales Support, Operations, and eBusiness/Internet Solutions. </p><a id=complinks href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/Companies/CompanyDetails.aspx?HHName=CareerlannersInc123445">Learn More about CareerPlanners, Inc</a><br><a href=http://www.careerplanners.com/index.cfm id=complinks>Visit Our Website</a><br><!--<a href="#" id="complinks">Company links</a> <br /><br />--><br><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td><span class=job_title>Senior Java Engineer<br></span></td><td align=right class=apply>   <a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/ApplyStart.aspx?Job_DID=J8F4H0649LXV051572S" onclick="CB.AskInfoBox.tallyApplyNowClick('AQ203S6D1Y034HXPV96');" class=btnJobSkin title="Apply for this job now!">Apply Now</a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_cbhlJobFeedback rel=nofollow target=_blank href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/accessible/jobfeedback.aspx?Job_DID=J8F4H0649LXV051572S">Report It</a></span></td></tr></table><p class=header>Job Description </p><div class=job_desc><div class=RichText_Content><p><span style="text-decoration: underline"></span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="text-decoration: underline">Primary responsibilities include:</span></p><ul><li><div>Responsible for part of the development of a software securities trading system. </div></li><li><div>Participate in the requirements analysis, conceptual design, detailed design, and implementation of a system. </div></li><li><div>Participate in integration testing of programs within a system. </div></li><li><div>Generate formal design documentation. </div></li><li>Support the development of Acceptance Test Plan and Procedures documents. </li></ul><p><span style="text-decoration: underline"><br> Technical Requirements: <p>&nbsp;</p><ul></ul></span></p><ul><li><p>Java and J2EE experience </p></li><li><p>The FIX protocol, and/or other aspects of the brokerage industry is a plus.</p></li><li><p>Design and development of applications using a development platform such as Streambase, etc </p></li><li><p>Experience using Java application servers such as BEA's WebLogic</p></li><li><p>Experience with Web Services concepts and implementation</p></li></ul></div> </div><br><br><p class=header>Job Requirements </p><div class=job_req><div class=RichText_Content>The primary focus of this Senior Java Engineer is to develop software application solutions that integrate securities trading systems, decision support, collaboration, as well as other core capabilities.  They rely heavily on internal expertise in the key areas of the financial industry.<br><br> The hiring company possesses world class technical talent and industry expertise in system concept development, rapid prototyping, software engineering, systems integration, and project leadership.  They pride themselves on their proven ability to apply their small, elite technical team focused on the end user solving problems quickly and effectively.</div> </div><p> </p><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td> </td><td align=right class=apply>   <a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/ApplyStart.aspx?Job_DID=J8F4H0649LXV051572S" onclick="CB.AskInfoBox.tallyApplyNowClick('AQ203S6D1Y034HXPV96');" class=btnJobSkin title="Apply for this job now!">Apply Now</a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_cbhlJobFeedback rel=nofollow target=_blank href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/accessible/jobfeedback.aspx?Job_DID=J8F4H0649LXV051572S">Report It</a></span></td></tr></table><br><br><div class=jd_jobprivacy style="border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 3px 3px 0px; margin-left: 10px;"><font style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; color: #000000;"><strong>CareerBuilder.com's Advice</strong></font><br><br><table id=_JobDetailsv2_tblPrivacyBox border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tbody><tr valign=top><td valign=top width=30><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/JS/Icons/lock.gif></td><td valign=top><span id=privacy>For your<a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/Info/Privacy.htm?sc_cmp1=js_jobdetails_privacy"> privacy and protection</a>, when applying to a job online:<br>Never give your social security number to a prospective employer, provide credit card or bank account information, or perform any sort of monetary transaction. &nbsp;<a href=/JobSeeker/Info/Privacy.aspx style="color: #336666;">Learn More<span style="text-decoration: none;">&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</sp