=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td colspan=2 valign=top><p class=header2>Job Overview</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 valign=top class=overview_nav><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=2><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Company:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks><a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/Companies/CompanyDetails.aspx?HHName=wwwcotscom" title="Click Here to Navigate To the Company Web Site">COmputing TechnologieS, Inc.</a></td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Base Pay: </td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>$64,000 - $66,000 /Year</td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Other Pay:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks></td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Employee Type:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>Full-Time</td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Industry:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>Computer Software<br> Computer Hardware</td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Manages Others: </td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>No</td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Job Type:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>Information Technology<br> Government - Federal</td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Required Education:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>4 Year Degree</td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Required Experience:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>5 to 8 years</td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Required Travel:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>Negligible</td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Relocation Covered:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks>No</td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Reference ID: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>Not Available </td></tr><tr><td width=50% valign=top class=overview_nav>Location:</td><td width=50% valign=top id=overviewlinks><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobLocation0_cbhlMapJob class=BingMap rel=nofollow href="#lat=38.955,lon=-94.5716,mapsize=small,thumbnailmap=False,streetlevel=False,maptoken="><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/JS/jobresults/mapit.gif id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobLocation0_imgMapIt alt="map it!">US-MO-Kansas City</a><iframe id=iframeForInlineMap frameborder=0 scrolling=no style=display:none;></iframe><div id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobLocation0_pnlLoadingMap class=loadingMap style=display:none;><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/js/widgets/loading.gif id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobLocation0_imgLoadingMap class=imgLoadingMap><br> Loading Map... </div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 align=center><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobMap0_cbhlMapJob class=BingMap rel=nofollow href="#lat=38.955,lon=-94.5716,mapsize=small,thumbnailmap=True,streetlevel=True,maptoken="></a><iframe id=iframeForInlineMap frameborder=0 scrolling=no style=display:none;></iframe><div id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobMap0_pnlLoadingMap class=loadingMap><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/js/widgets/loading.gif id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobMap0_imgLoadingMap class=imgLoadingMap><br> Loading Map... </div></td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav> </td><td valign=top>  </td></tr><!--End Job Overview Table--><!--Begin Contact Info Table--><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Contact: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>Scott MacDonald </td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Phone: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>Not Available </td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Email: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks><a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/ApplyStart.aspx?Job_DID=J8H2B06DV3L6FLLPTGC">Send Email Now</a></td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>Fax: </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks>Not Available </td></tr><tr><td valign=top class=overview_nav>  </td><td valign=top id=overviewlinks></td></tr><tr><td> </td></tr><tr><td> </td></tr></table><!--End Contact Info Table--></td></tr><tr><td style="padding-top:30px; padding-bottom:20px;"><!--$JobSkinImage04$--></td></tr></table></td><td valign=top><table width=480 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=20><tr><td><p class=header2> Company Overview </p><p><strong>COmputing TechnologieS, Inc.</strong> is a Virginia corporation founded in 1992.  CoTs is primarily engaged in information systems engineering through systems analysis, design and development, test and evaluation, and operations and maintenance of computer-based applications.</p><p>Our revenue projections show strong growth.  We believe they will show even more growth because we are continuously competing for new contracts and follow-on contracts for current services.</p><p>Over the next ten years, CoTs hopes to maintain a slow, deliberate growth, affording employees a professional atmosphere and a high-tech environment in which we can deliver quality engineering, analytical, and technical services to all our customers.</p><p>CoTs is committed to being fair and objective to all employees.  We value everyone on the CoTs team.  CoTs management intends to treat all employees with respect and professionalism.  Our view of the management-employee relationship begins with the understanding that first, and foremost, it is a relationship based on mutual trust and confidence.  Management must be committed to constantly improving the workplace, the practices, and the policies of CoTs.  Employees must be committed to giving their best effort and to providing products and services in accordance with our contracts.  Management expects employees to seek ways to improve their individual professionalism, expand their expertise, and enhance the productivity of CoTs.</p><p>Our philosophy can thus be stated simply: CoTs management provides opportunities for professional and technical work; you, in turn, can enjoy a rewarding career capitalizing upon these opportunities. </p><p> </p><p class=comp_over><a id=complinks href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/Companies/CompanyDetails.aspx?HHName=wwwcotscom">Learn More about COmputing TechnologieS, Inc.</a><br><a href=http://www.cots.com id=complinks>http://www.cots.com</a><br><br><br></p><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td><span class=job_title>Mainframe Developer</span></td><td align=right class=apply>   <a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/AOReviewReq.aspx?Job_DID=J8H2B06DV3L6FLLPTGC" onclick="CB.AskInfoBox.tallyApplyNowClick('AQ210F75QVX233NDFQK');" class=btnJobSkin title="Apply for this job now!">Apply Now</a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_cbhlJobFeedback rel=nofollow target=_blank href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/accessible/jobfeedback.aspx?Job_DID=J8H2B06DV3L6FLLPTGC">Report It</a></span></td></tr></table><p class=header>Job Description </p><div class=job_desc><div class=RichText_Content><p style="text-align: justify">As a  Member of a system development/maintenance team that supports Department of Defense integrated financial and personnel resource management systems. This staff member will design, develop, and implement integrated solutions for a complex, mainframe based personnel and pay system.<br><br></p><p style="text-align: justify">Staff Member will analyze all aspects of mainframe resource use with the objective of reducing mainframe processing costs.  Must be able to identify processes, procedures, and program code that consumes more mainframe resources than necessary. Monitors overall mainframe resource usage and makes recommendations to reduce I/O, storage, and CPU charges and improve storeage management.</p><p style="text-align: justify"><br> Experienced mainframe programming/analysis with detailed knowledge of <strong>COBOL</strong>, <strong>SQL, DB2, JCL, VSAM, and Oracle</strong> required. Knowledge of <strong>ROSCOE</strong> and <strong>Librarian</strong> a plus.</p><p style="text-align: justify"><br> CoTs is an Equal Opportunity Employer and Affirmative Action Employer - M/F/Vet/Disab</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><br><br><p class=header>Job Requirements </p><div class=job_req><div class=RichText_Content><ul><li>Bachelor's degree in computer science, or related field preferred or equivalent combination of education and experience </li><li>Full Scope background check </li><li>US Citizenship </li><li>44 hour work </li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><p> </p><table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td> </td><td align=right class=apply>   <a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/ApplyOnline/AOReviewReq.aspx?Job_DID=J8H2B06DV3L6FLLPTGC" onclick="CB.AskInfoBox.tallyApplyNowClick('AQ210F75QVX233NDFQK');" class=btnJobSkin title="Apply for this job now!">Apply Now</a><br><span id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_jobFeedbackWrapper style=padding-right:4px;><a id=JobDetails_ucJobDetailsSkin__JobSkinContent_ucJobFeedback_cbhlJobFeedback rel=nofollow target=_blank href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/accessible/jobfeedback.aspx?Job_DID=J8H2B06DV3L6FLLPTGC">Report It</a></span></td></tr></table><br><br><div class=jd_jobprivacy style="border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 3px 3px 0px; margin-left: 10px;"><font style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; color: #000000;"><strong>CareerBuilder.com's Advice</strong></font><br><br><table id=_JobDetailsv2_tblPrivacyBox border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tbody><tr valign=top><td valign=top width=30><img src=http://img.icbdr.com/images/JS/Icons/lock.gif></td><td valign=top><span id=privacy>For your<a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/JobSeeker/Info/Privacy.htm?sc_cmp1=js_jobdetails_privacy"> privacy and protection</a>, when applying to a job online:<br>Never give your social security number to a prospective employer, provide credit card or bank account information, or perform any sort of monetary transaction. &nbsp;<a href=/JobSeeker/Info/Privacy.aspx style="color: #336666;">Learn More<span style="text-decoration: none;">&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</span></a><br><br>By applying to a job using CareerBuilder.com you are agreeing to comply with and be subject to the CareerBuilder.com<a href=http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/info/hhterms.htm> Terms and Conditions</a> for use of our website. To use our website, you must agree with the <a href=http://www.careerbuilder.com/jobseeker/info/hhterms.htm> Terms and Conditions</a> and both meet and comply with their provisions.</span></td></tr></tbody></table><br></div></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 height=5 bgcolor=#a9b0c1><!--$FooterImage$--></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><script type=text/javascript language=javascript>
